<s> THIS IS ALEXANDRIA VIRGINIA IN THE MIDDLE EIGHTEEN HUNDREDS </s>
<s> THIS IS ALEXANDRIA TODAY </s>
<s> NOTICE ANY DIFFERENCE </s>
<s> WELL THERE'S NOT MUCH </s>
<s> FOR THE MOST PART THE CITY'S DESIGN HAS REMAINED UNCHANGED </s>
<s> STREETS ARE SET UP WITH SEVERAL ALTERNATIVE ROUTES </s>
<s> THERE ARE TREE LINED SIDEWALKS AND SHORT BLOCKS VERY INVITING TO PEDESTRIANS </s>
<s> BUILDINGS COMPATIBLE IN SIZE ARE GROUPED TOGETHER </s>
<s> ONE MIGHT BE A STORE WHILE NEXT DOOR IS A RESIDENCE AND ACROSS THE STREET PERHAPS A SCHOOL </s>
<s> DOES THIS LOOK LIKE YOUR TOWN </s>
<s> IN MANY CASES PROBABLY NOT </s>
<s> IN TIMES PAST CITY LEADERS ZONED ACCORDING TO BUILDING SIZE AND DESIGN AND NOT FUNCTION </s>
<s> THAT MEANT ONE BLOCK OF BUILDINGS COULD HAVE MANY USES </s>
<s> THE IDEA IS MAKING A COMEBACK </s>
<s> URBAN PLANNERS IN PARTICULAR HAVE BEEN VERY INTERESTED IN RECENT YEARS IN LOOKING AT WHAT'S CALLED MIXED USE DEVELOPMENT WHERE YOU DON'T HAVE JUST RESIDENTIAL AREAS IN ONE ZONE AND RETAIL OFFICE IN ANOTHER ZONE BUT YOU REALLY HAVE A MIXTURE OF LAND USES </s>
<s> SO RESIDENTS CAN WALK TO NEARBY SHOPS WALK OR RIDE BIKES TO GET TO WORK SCHOOL OR THE RAPID TRANSIT </s>
<s> SOMEHOW WE GOT AWAY FROM THIS KIND OF URBAN DESIGN </s>
<s> MOST CURRENT ZONING CODES REQUIRE SHOPPING MALLS AND OFFICES BE PLACED IN A COMMERCIAL DISTRICT USUALLY A GOOD DISTANCE FROM THE NEAREST HOME </s>
<s> THESE AND OTHER FACTORS LEAD TO URBAN SPRAWL TRANSLATION GETTING INTO A CAR AND DRIVING AND ULTIMATELY BEING OUT OF TOUCH WITH YOUR NEIGHBORS </s>
