<s> IN SUNDAY'S NEW YORK TIMES IT WAS ARGUED THAT NO MATTER WHO WAS PRESIDENT FIDEL CASTRO HAS HELD THE UPPER HAND </s>
<s> IS THAT TRUE </s>
<s> I WOULDN'T CALL IT UPPER HAND BUT WE CERTAINLY HAD TO DEAL WITH HIM FOR A LONG LONG TIME </s>
<s> AND HE HAS FROM TIME TO TIME GIVEN HEADACHES TO VIRTUALLY EVERY PRESIDENT THAT'S BEEN IN OFFICE SINCE DWIGHT EISENHOWER </s>
<s> IS THERE ANY LESSONS FROM PAST ADMINISTRATIONS THAT PRESIDENT CLINTON CAN DRAW ON IN DEALING WITH THE CURRENT CUBAN CRISIS </s>
<s> NO I THINK THIS ONE IS UNIQUE </s>
<s> IN THIS PARTICULAR SITUATION UNLIKE THE BULK OF THE HISTORY OF CASTRO'S REGIME IN CUBA THE COLD WAR'S OVER AND THE RUSSIANS ARE NO LONGER SUBSIDIZING CUBA </s>
<s> THE CUBAN ECONOMY IS ON ITS OWN AND IN A DISASTROUS STATE OF FALL SO I THINK THIS IS A SPECIAL SITUATION </s>
<s> PREVIOUS LESSONS ARE NOT REALLY APPLICABLE HERE </s>
<s> SO COULD THAT MEAN AS WELL THAT PRESIDENT CLINTON COULD GO IN AND ACTUALLY GAIN THE UPPER HAND </s>
<s> WELL I DON'T THINK IT'S GOING TO BE CLINTON THAT'S GOING TO GAIN THE UPPER HAND I THINK IT'S THE DESTRUCTION OF THE CUBAN ECONOMY THAT IS ERODING CASTRO'S SUPPORT AND PULLING THE CUBAN POLITICAL SYSTEM APART </s>
<s> MY OWN VIEW IS THAT WE OUGHT TO ENCOURAGE THAT NOT BY MAKING LIFE MORE DIFFICULT FOR THE POOR PEOPLE OF CUBA BUT RATHER BY OPENING CUBA AS WAS THE CASE WITH RESPECT TO THE SOVIET UNION TO THE WINDS OF CHANGE FROM OUTSIDE AND INCREASING EXPANDING TRADE AND FIRST OF ALL EXCHANGE WITH CUBA </s>
<s> DOES THE UNITED STATES INITIATE THOSE TALKS </s>
<s> YES I THINK SO </s>
<s> I WOULD EXPAND THE AGENDA OF THE TALKS THAT ARE GOING TO START TOMORROW IN NEW YORK TO GO BEYOND IMMIGRATION TO DISCUSS VERY CLEARLY THE STEPS THE UNITED STATES WOULD LIKE TO SEE OCCURRING IN CUBA TOWARDS OPENING THE ECONOMY AND EXPANDING DEMOCRATIC OPPORTUNITIES TO THE PEOPLE OF CUBA </s>
<s> I WOULD NOT EXPECT VERY MUCH FROM CASTRO IN THAT RESPECT </s>
<s> BUT I WOULD ON THE OTHER HAND UNILATERALLY EXPAND THOSE OPPORTUNITIES FOR TRADE AND PERSONAL EXCHANGE ALL BY MYSELF IF I WERE THE PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES </s>
<s> NOW WHAT OF THIS LATEST REPORT THIS MORNING OF PROPOSAL TO OFFER UP TO TWENTY THOUSAND RESIDENTIAL VISAS TO CUBANS </s>
<s> IS THAT ENOUGH TO STOP AT LEAST THE FLOW AT THIS TIME OF CUBAN REFUGEES </s>
<s> I WOULDN'T BE SURPRISED TO SEE THE FLOW OF CUBAN REFUGEES DECLINE IN PART BECAUSE OF THE POTENTIAL FOR EXPANDED ACCESS THROUGH INCREASE IN THE NUMBER OF VISA GRANTS </s>
<s> ALSO IN PART BECAUSE IT'S NOW BECOMING OBVIOUS TO THE CUBANS THAT THE FATE OF THOSE WHO TAKE TO THE BOATS IS GOING TO BE GUANTANAMO RATHER THAN MIAMI </s>
<s> SO YOU THINK THAT'S GOING TO BE ENOUGH </s>
<s> WE'VE BEEN SEEING IN THE PAST FEW DAYS AS A MATTER OF FACT A DECREASE IN THE NUMBER OF CUBAN REFUGEES SETTING OUT OR SETTING SAIL TO THE UNITED STATES </s>
<s> DO YOU THINK THAT THAT WAS CAUSED MANY PEOPLE HAVE ATTRIBUTED THAT TO BAD WEATHER DO YOU THINK MORE OR LESS IT'S BECAUSE OF THIS POLICY THAT WAS INITIATED OR IMPOSED BY THE CLINTON ADMINISTRATION </s>
<s> I THINK IT WILL BE IN THE FUTURE </s>
<s> FRANKLY I DO NOT EXPECT THE SAME LEVEL OF CUBANS TO TRY TO GO TO THE BOATS AS HAS BEEN THE CASE IN THE MONTH OF AUGUST </s>
<s> YOU KNOW WE PICKED UP AND MOVED TO GUANTANAMO ABOUT SEVENTEEN OR EIGHTEEN THOUSAND </s>
<s> THE EXPANDED NUMBERS OF VISAS WILL BE SOMETHING IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD OF TWENTY THOUSAND WHICH IS ABOUT EQUIVALENT TO ONE MONTH AND A LITTLE BIT PLUS OF THE CUBANS WHO HAVE BEEN MOVING SO FAR </s>
<s> I THINK IT WILL BE THE FACT THAT THEY'RE GOING TO GO TO GUANTANAMO THAT WILL DO THE TRICK </s>
<s> BUT A DECLINE IN THE NUMBER OF BOAT PEOPLE WILL NOT SOLVE THE PROBLEM IN MY JUDGEMENT </s>
<s> IT'S A LONGER RANGE PROBLEM AND ONE THAT THE CLINTON ADMINISTRATION IS GOING TO HAVE TO FACE UP TO </s>
<s> THIS IS THE PRESENT SITUATION IN MY JUDGMENT IS ONLY A VERY INTERIM SOLUTION </s>
<s> INITIATIVES WITH CUBA IN THE PAST HAVE ALL FALLEN APART </s>
<s> WHAT NEEDS TO TAKE PLACE THAT WE ARE MORE SUCCESSFUL NOW AS WELL AS IN THE FUTURE </s>
<s> WELL I THINK THAT WHAT OUGHT TO TAKE PLACE AS I SUGGESTED BEFORE IS NOT A TIGHTENING OF THE EMBARGO BUT RATHER A UNILATERAL RELAXATION OF OUR BAN ON EXCHANGE OF GOODS AND PEOPLE WITH CUBA </s>
<s> YOU KNOW WE'RE QUITE UNIQUE IN THE WORLD IN RESPECT OF CUBA </s>
<s> BRITAIN THE EUROPEAN COUNTRIES JAPAN ALL TRADE WITH CUBA </s>
<s> LATIN AMERICAN IS IN FAVOR OF DROPPING THE EMBARGO WITH CUBA </s>
<s> THE UNITED STATES STANDS OUT ALL ALONE AMONG THE FAMILY OF NATIONS IN ATTEMPTING TO EMBARGO THAT COUNTRY </s>
<s> DO YOU THINK PRESIDENT CLINTON IS READY TO TAKE THAT STAND THOUGH DO YOU THINK HE WILL GO THAT FAR </s>
<s> OR WILL HE JUST CONCENTRATE MAINLY ON IMMIGRATION ISSUES </s>
<s> NO I THINK IT'S HIGHLY UNLIKELY THAT THIS ADMINISTRATION WILL TAKE THAT STEP LARGELY BECAUSE THE CONSEQUENCES POLITICALLY IN FLORIDA WHICH IS OF COURSE A CRITICAL STATE FOR THE CLINTON ASPIRATION IN THIS ELECTION AND ALSO THE NEXT PRESIDENTIAL ELECTION </s>
<s> O. K. WILLIAM ROGERS WE THANK YOU FOR JOINING US THIS MORNING FROM WASHINGTON </s>
<s> THREE YEARS AFTER HIS DEATH BRITISH MOVIE DIRECTOR TONY RICHARDSON IS BEING HONORED IN NEW YORK </s>
<s> C. N. N.'S CYNTHIA TORNQUIST REPORTS ON A CREATIVE TALENT WHOSE FAMILY IS AS WELL KNOWN AS HIS WORK </s>
<s> BEST KNOWN FOR THE MULTI ACADEMY AWARD WINNING TOM JONES BRITISH DIRECTOR TONY RICHARDSON DIRECTED THE LONELINESS OF THE LONG DISTANCE RUNNER LOOK BACK IN ANGER AND THE HOTEL NEW HAMPSHIRE </s>
<s> HE WAS A GREAT MAN A GREAT FRIEND AND A GREAT DIRECTOR </s>
<s> AND I THINK THE ONE THING THAT HE WAS ABLE TO DO WAS KIND OF MIX THINGS THAT ARE QUITE FANTASTICAL WITH THINGS THAT ARE QUITE MUNDANE </s>
<s> RICHARDSON BEGAN HIS CAREER IN THE TELEVISION AND THEATER BECOMING A MAJOR FILMMAKING FORCE IN THE MID NINETEEN FIFTIES </s>
<s> HE PROJECTED A NEW VISION OF LIFE ON THE BIG SCREEN AND THE REALISM OF HIS WORK AND THAT OF HIS PEERS EARNED THEM THE LABEL OF THE ANGRY YOUNG MEN </s>
<s> HE CHANGED MOVIES BECAUSE HE STARTED MAKING MOVIES IN ENGLAND AT A TIME WHEN IT WAS A NEW VOICE IT WAS A NEW WAY OF LOOKING AT THINGS </s>
<s> RICHARDSON DIED IN NINETEEN NINETY ONE OF AIDS LEAVING BEHIND TWO SUCCESSFUL ACTRESS DAUGHTERS NATASHA AND JOELY RICHARDSON BY HIS MARRIAGE TO VANESSA REDGRAVE </s>
<s> RECENTLY THEY AND OTHERS WHO WORKED WITH THE DIRECTOR GATHERED IN NEW YORK FOR THE WORLD PREMIER OF RICHARDSON'S LAST FILM BLUE SKY </s>
<s> HE WAS NEVER SOMEBODY WHO YOU KNOW SAID HOW GREAT THEY WERE </s>
<s> IT WAS HE COULD ONLY SEE FLAWS </s>
<s> ALL OF US COULD ONLY SEE THAT THIS WAS ONE OF THE MOST SPECIAL MOVIES THAT HE MADE </s>
<s> DON'T YOU TOUCH ME </s>
<s> DON'T YOU TOUCH ME </s>
<s> I WOULDN'T LET ANYBODY HURT YOU </s>
<s> SCHEDULED FOR RELEASE THIS SEPTEMBER BLUE SKY STARS JESSICA LANGE AND TOMMY LEE JONES </s>
<s> IT TELLS THE STORY OF A BEAUTIFUL WOMAN WHOSE SENSUALITY AND NEED FOR ATTENTION LANDS HER HUSBAND IN TROUBLE JUST AS HE'S ABOUT TO EXPOSE A MILITARY COVER UP </s>
<s> GET YOUR GODDAMED CONTAMINATED HANDS OFF ME </s>
<s> TIMED WITH THE RELEASE OF BLUE SKY THE FILM SOCIETY OF LINCOLN CENTER IS LAUNCHING A RETROSPECTIVE OF RICHARDSON'S FILMS WHICH RUNS THROUGH SEPTEMBER THIRTEENTH </s>
