<s> THE AMERICAN ASSOCIATION OF RETIRED PERSONS </s>
<s> I'M ASKING YOU TO JOIN US </s>
<s> THIRTY THREE MILLION MEMBERS STRONG </s>
<s> MY NAME IS HERBERT BENGEMAN </s>
<s> I LIVE IN NORTH LITTLE ROCK </s>
<s> AN ANNUAL INCOME OF MORE THAN A THIRD OF A BILLION DOLLARS </s>
<s> I AM THELMA HEMMONS OF WEST HELENA ARKANSAS </s>
<s> A NONPROFIT ASSOCIATION MAKING SO MUCH MONEY IT'S NOW RUNNING INTO TROUBLE ON ITS TAXES </s>
<s> FOR EIGHT DOLLARS ANYONE FIFTY OR OLDER CAN JOIN </s>
<s> IT'S BECOME ONE OF THE MOST POWERFUL LOBBYING GROUPS IN THE COUNTRY </s>
<s> A. A. R. P. HAS BEEN A CONSTANT VOICE CALLING FOR COMPREHENSIVE REFORM OF THE NATION'S HEALTH CARE SYSTEM </s>
<s> BUT A. A. R. P. DOES MORE THAN JUST LOBBY </s>
<s> THROUGH THE LARGEST CIRCULATION MAGAZINE IN THE UNITED STATES MODERN MATURITY ITS NONPROFIT NAME IS USED TO MARKET PRESCRIPTION DRUGS AN INVESTMENT PLAN CREDIT CARDS INSURANCE PAGES FULL OF ADS </s>
<s> THE ASSOCIATION REALLY TRIES TO USE ITS AVAILABLE RESOURCES TO GO OUT INTO THE FIELD TO BENEFIT ITS MEMBERS TO EDUCATE ITS MEMBERS AND TO PROVIDE VALUABLE SERVICE </s>
<s> BUT LESS THAN HALF OF A. A. R. P.'S INCOME IS FROM MEMBERSHIP FEES </s>
<s> IN FACT LAST YEAR A. A. R. P. PROMOTED PRODUCTS THAT COMPETE AGAINST FOR PROFIT BUSINESSES GENERATED ONE HUNDRED EIGHTY SIX MILLION DOLLARS </s>
<s> THAT'S INCOME THE I. R. S. DID NOT TAX IN PAST YEARS </s>
<s> NOW THE INTERNAL REVENUE SERVICE HAS DECIDED THE ASSOCIATION SHOULD PAY ITS FAIR SHARE </s>
<s> ON WHAT IS BARELY A FOOTNOTE TO ITS NINETEEN NINETY THREE ANNUAL REPORT A. A. R. P. DISCLOSES A ONE HUNDRED THIRTY FIVE MILLION DOLLAR PAYMENT TO THE I. R. S. LAST APRIL </s>
<s> THIS HUGE LUMP SUM PAYMENT IS FOR TAXES ON CERTAIN INCOME RECEIVED BETWEEN NINETEEN EIGHTY FIVE AND NINETEEN NINETY THREE </s>
<s> THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS OF A. A. R. P. FELT THAT IT WAS IN THE BEST INTEREST OF THE ORGANIZATION TO PUT THE YEARS THAT WERE IN QUESTION BEHIND US TO REACH A NEGOTIATED AGREEMENT WITH THE INTERNAL REVENUE SERVICE </s>
