<s> I SENT TO SOME COMPANIES FOR BROCHURES AND RECEIVED ANSWERS SAYING THEY WOULD ONLY MEN </s>
<s> MOST OF MY FRIENDS WHO VISIT COMPANIES WERE TOLD COMPANIES WON'T HIRE WOMEN THIS YEAR </s>
<s> AND AT INTERVIEWS SOME WERE TOLD THEIR LEGS WERE FAT </s>
<s> SOME WERE ASKED IF THEY HAD BOYFRIENDS AND IF SO HOW MUCH INVOLVEMENT THEY HAD WITH THEM </s>
<s> SOME STUDIES SHOW THE JOBLESS RATE FOR RECENT WOMEN GRADUATES AS HIGH AS FORTY PERCENT </s>
<s> GLAMOROUS OR NOT BLUE COLLAR OPPORTUNITIES FOR WOMEN DO EXIST IN JAPAN </s>
<s> AND IN SOME FIELDS THEY'RE SLOWLY INCREASING </s>
<s> NOWADAYS THE RESPONSIBILITIES OF FEMALE OFFICERS HAVE EXPANDED </s>
<s> WE GET TO DO MORE THINGS LIKE WORKING AT A STATION OR PATROLLING IN A CAR </s>
<s> ONLY MEN USED TO DO THOSE JOBS BEFORE </s>
<s> BUT PROGRESS FOR YOUNG JAPANESE WOMEN IN HIGHER PAYING CAREERS IS ANOTHER STORY </s>
<s> THE MAJORITY OF JOBS FOR WOMEN IN JAPAN REMAIN LOW LEVEL OFFICE POSITIONS BUT IT'S A LONG WAY FROM ANSWERING TELEPHONES TO MAKING EXECUTIVE DECISIONS </s>
<s> THAT KIND OF WORK IS STILL DOMINATED BY MEN </s>
<s> MANY ARGUE THAT WHITE COLLAR POSITIONS WILL OPEN UP FOR WOMEN NOT BECAUSE OF ANY SOCIETAL SENSE OF FAIRNESS BUT BECAUSE OF SOCIETAL NEED </s>
<s> JAPAN'S POPULATION IS AGING </s>
<s> DEMOGRAPHICS SHOW THE COUNTRY IS HEADED FOR AN OVERALL SHORTAGE OF WORKERS </s>
<s> THE JAPANESE HAVE TWO WAYS TO MEET THEIR LABOR SHORTAGE TWO PRACTICAL WAYS </s>
<s> ONE IS TO ALLOW FREER IMMIGRATION INTO JAPAN </s>
<s> THE SECOND OF COURSE IS TO BETTER UTILIZE WOMEN </s>
<s> AND I THINK THE JAPANESE WILL CHOOSE THE LATTER </s>
<s> EVENTUALLY IT'S THE IMMEDIATE FUTURE THAT BOTHERS YOUNG WOMEN SUCH AS YOKO YAMAMOTO </s>
<s> SHE SAYS SHE DOES EXPECT WORKPLACE EQUALITY BETWEEN THE SEXES IN JAPAN BUT IN HER WORDS PROBABLY NOT IN MY LIFETIME. BILL DORMAN C. N. N. BUSINESS NEWS TOKYO </s>
