<s> BUT WHAT IS CERTAIN IS THAT WITH EACH PASSING DAY THE RAFTS ARE BECOMING INCREASINGLY SOPHISTICATED </s>
<s> JOHN ZARRELLA C. N. N. COJIMAR CUBA </s>
<s> A U. S. LED MILITARY INVASION OF HAITI LOOKS MORE LIKELY </s>
<s> THE U. S. HAS FORMED A COALITION WITH BARBADOS TRINIDAD ANTIGUA THE BAHAMAS GUYANA JAMAICA AND BELIZE </s>
<s> NOW A DISCUSSION ABOUT U. S. POLICY TOWARD HAITI AND THE POSSIBILITY OF AN INVASION </s>
<s> WE'RE JOINED IN NEW YORK BY STEPHEN SOLARZ A FORMER U. S. REPRESENTATIVE FROM NEW YORK </s>
<s> HE CURRENTLY IS A VISITING PROFESSOR OF INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS AT GEORGE WASHINGTON UNIVERSITY IN WASHINGTON D. C. </s>
<s> AND HERE IN WASHINGTON IS DOUG BANDOW A SENIOR FELLOW AT THE CATO INSTITUTE WHO SERVED AS A DOMESTIC POLICY ADVISER TO PRESIDENT REAGAN </s>
<s> THANK YOU BOTH FOR JOINING US </s>
<s> MR. SOLARZ DO YOU THINK IT'S TIME FOR THE U. S. TO INVADE </s>
<s> I THINK WE HAVE APPROACHED THE POINT WHERE WE OUGHT TO TOGETHER WITH OTHER COUNTRIES RESTORE DEMOCRACY TO HAITI BY SENDING IN A MULTINATIONAL FORCE </s>
<s> WHY IS THIS THE MOMENT </s>
<s> FIRST BECAUSE I DON'T THINK WE CAN JUSTIFY ANY LONGER DESTROYING A COUNTRY IN ORDER TO SAVE IT </s>
<s> THE EMBARGO WE HAVE IMPOSED ON HAITI HAS REDUCED WHAT WAS THE POOREST COUNTRY IN THE HEMISPHERE TO BEGIN WITH TO AN EVEN MORE DESPERATE STATE OF POVERTY THAN EXISTED BEFORE </s>
<s> FURTHERMORE THE REGIME HAS INDICATED IN ITS LATEST MOVE WHICH WAS THE ASSASSINATION OF A CATHOLIC PRIEST THAT IT LITERALLY ACCEPTS NO RESTRAINTS WHATSOEVER ON ITS BEHAVIOR AND SINCE THE ADMINISTRATION HAS MADE IT FAIRLY CLEAR THAT IT IS NOT PREPARED TO TOLERATE THE CONTINUED EXISTENCE OF A MILITARY JUNTA IN HAITI I THINK IT WOULD BE BETTER TO MOVE SOONER RATHER THAN LATER SO THAT WE CAN BRING THE AGONY OF THE HAITIAN PEOPLE TO AN END </s>
<s> LET'S HEAR MR. BANDOW'S RESPONSE TO THAT </s>
<s> WELL IT'S OBVIOUS WE CAN END THE AGONY OF THE HAITIAN PEOPLE BY GETTING RID OF THE EMBARGO </s>
<s> I THINK THE FORMER CONGRESSMAN IS RIGHT ABOUT THE PERNICIOUS EFFECTS OF THAT EMBARGO ON THE PEOPLE THERE </s>
<s> THE REAL ISSUE THOUGH IS WHY AN INVASION </s>
<s> THERE ARE A LOT OF PLACES AROUND THE GLOBE THAT AREN'T DEMOCRATIC </s>
<s> THERE ARE A LOT OF PLACES THAT VIOLATE HUMAN RIGHTS EVEN WORSE THAN IN HAITI I MEAN LOOK NEXT DOOR TO CUBA </s>
<s> THE QUESTION IS SHOULD THE UNITED STATES PUT ITS YOUNG PEOPLE AT RISK TO TRY TO RESTORE DEMOCRACY ESPECIALLY IN A PLACE THAT'S NEVER HAD DEMOCRACY </s>
<s> I MEAN AN INVASION IS MERELY THE FIRST STEP NOT THE LAST STEP </s>
<s> YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO GO DOWN THERE AND TRY TO CREATE DEMOCRATIC INSTITUTIONS CREATE AN ETHOS OF DEMOCRACY </s>
<s> WE SAW HOW HARD THAT IS IN SOMALIA </s>
<s> I THINK IT WOULD BE EXTRAORDINARILY FOOLISH </s>
<s> THERE'S JUST NO REASON AT STAKE FOR THE UNITED STATES TO PUT ITS PEOPLE AT RISK IN AN INVASION LIKE THIS </s>
<s> IT WON'T GAIN US ANYTHING </s>
<s> MR. SOLARZ IS HAITI WORTH THE LOSS OF U. S. LIFE </s>
<s> I RATHER DOUBT THAT THERE WILL BE MUCH LOSS OF AMERICAN LIFE IF WE WERE TO INTERVENE MILITARILY </s>
<s> IF DESERT STORM TOOK SIX WEEKS I THINK THAT CARIBBEAN HURRICANE IF I CAN COIN A PHRASE WOULD TAKE SIX HOURS </s>
<s> I FULLY AGREE WITH MR. BANDOW THAT WE CAN'T CONSTITUTE OURSELVES AS THE POLICEMEN FOR THE ENTIRE WORLD AND INTERVENE IN ORDER TO ESTABLISH OR RESTORE DEMOCRACY EVERYWHERE AROUND THE GLOBE BUT IN THE CASE OF HAITI THE SECURITY COUNCIL OF THE UNITED NATIONS HAS ALREADY AUTHORIZED THE USE OF FORCE IF THAT SHOULD BE NECESSARY TO RESTORE DEMOCRACY THERE </s>
<s> TODAY THE OTHER COUNTRIES OF THE CARIBBEAN JOINED WITH US IN COMMITTING FORCES TO SUCH AN ENTERPRISE </s>
<s> THE O. A. S. WANTS THE RESTORATION OF DEMOCRACY IN HAITI </s>
<s> THIS IS AN ENTIRELY DOABLE AND ACHIEVABLE OBJECTIVE </s>
<s> I DO NOT BELIEVE IT WILL RESULT IN THE LOSS OF ANY SIGNIFICANT NUMBER IF ANY AMERICAN LIVES AND THEREFORE I THINK WE SHOULD MAKE AN EFFORT TO RESTORE THE ONLY PERSON EVER ELECTED IN A TRULY FREE AND FAIR ELECTION IN HAITI TO THE PRESIDENCY OF THAT COUNTRY FATHER ARISTIDE </s>
<s> BUT THAT DOESN'T MAKE HIM A DEMOCRAT </s>
<s> I MEAN HE'S COMPARED HIMSELF TO ROBESPIERRE THE MURDEROUS HEAD OF THE FRENCH REVOLUTION </s>
<s> HE'S SOMEBODY WHO'S ENDORSED NECKLACING </s>
<s> I MEAN THIS IS SOMEBODY WHO IS BETTER THAN THE MILITARY JUNTA BUT WE CERTAINLY SHOULD NOT PAT OURSELVES ON THE BACK AND ACT AS IF HE IS THE BEST THAT HAITI CAN HAVE OR THAT HE REALLY IS WORTH AMERICAN LIES </s>
<s> AND THOUGH IN THE INITIAL STAGE ONE THINK WE CAN EASILY YOU KNOW WIN A VICTORY OVER THE HAITIAN MILITARY SUCH AS IT IS </s>
<s> THE QUESTION IS THE LONG TERM </s>
<s> THE LESSON FROM SOMALIA OF COURSE IS WHAT YOU DO IS YOU KILL A FEW AMERICANS AND YOU YOU KNOW DRAG THE BODIES THROUGH THE STREETS </s>
<s> MR. BANDOW IF YOU OPPOSE AN INVASION WHAT IS YOUR SOLUTION TO THE HAITI SITUATION </s>
<s> QUITE HONESTLY I THINK THERE ARE A LOT OF PLACES AROUND THE WORLD WHERE THERE AREN'T EASY SOLUTIONS </s>
<s> MY SOLUTION NUMBER ONE IS WE STOP WRECKING THEIR ECONOMY AND FURTHER IMPOVERISHING THESE DESPERATELY POOR PEOPLE </s>
<s> LIFT THE EMBARGO THEN </s>
<s> ABSOLUTELY </s>
<s> I MEAN WE'RE HURTING NOT THE JUNTA WE'RE HURTING THE POOR PEOPLE THERE </s>
<s> BUT I DON'T THINK THAT TRYING TO PUT BACK INTO POWER SOMEBODY WHO THOUGH DEMOCRATICALLY ELECTED IS NOT TERRIBLY DEMOCRATIC IN THE WAY HE OPERATES IS WORTH AN AWFUL LOT OF EFFORT FROM THIS COUNTRY </s>
<s> I MEAN THERE ARE A LOT OF MORE SERIOUS PROBLEMS IN THE WORLD </s>
<s> MR. SOLARZ IT'S TRUE THAT HAITI DOES NOT HAVE THE DEMOCRATIC INSTITUTIONS WHICH MIGHT SUPPORT A DEMOCRACY AFTER AN INVASION </s>
<s> HOW WOULD YOU DEAL WITH THAT SITUATION </s>
<s> WELL I THINK WE HAVE TO TAKE NOTE OF THE FACT THAT FATHER ARISTIDE WAS ELECTED PRESIDENT IN WHAT EVERYONE AGREED WAS A GENUINELY FREE AND FAIR ELECTION </s>
<s> THE MAN MAY NOT BE THE EMBODIMENT OF POLITICAL PERFECTION BUT DURING THE SEVEN MONTHS HE WAS IN POWER THE NUMBER OF PEOPLE TRYING TO FLEE HAITI BECAUSE OF REPRESSION WAS DIMINISHED THERE WERE RELATIVELY FEW HUMAN RIGHTS ABUSES AND I THINK THE PEOPLE OF HAITI DESERVE A CHANCE TO HAVE SOMEONE THEY ELECTED SERVE THEM AS THEIR LEADER </s>
<s> MR. BANDOW REFERRED TO WHAT MIGHT HAPPEN IN THE LONG RUN </s>
<s> I DON'T THINK THERE'S GOING TO HAVE TO BE A LONG RUN </s>
<s> OUR MILITARY PRESENCE THERE ONCE FATHER ARISTIDE IS RESTORED TO POWER CAN BE RELATIVELY BRIEF </s>
<s> ALL WE HAVE TO DO I BELIEVE IS TOGETHER WITH THE OTHER COUNTRIES THAT WOULD BE PART OF THIS MULTINATIONAL FORCE RECRUIT TRAIN EQUIP AND DEPLOY AN INDIGENOUS SECURITY FORCE CAPABLE OF MAINTAINING LAW AND ORDER AND PROTECTING THE REGIME AND THEN WITHDRAW </s>
<s> I DON'T THINK THAT SHOULD TAKE MORE THAN SEVERAL MONTHS </s>
<s> IT IS A DOABLE AND ENTIRELY ACHIEVABLE PROPOSITION </s>
<s> AND WE'RE GOING TO HAVE IT LEAVE IT THERE </s>
<s> STEPHEN SOLARZ FORMER U. S. REPRESENTATIVE AND DOUG BANDOW CATO INSTITUTION THANK YOU BOTH FOR COMING IN </s>
