<s> TWO GIANT U. S. DEFENSE CONTRACTORS ARE HEADING DOWN THE ROAD TOWARD A MEGA MERGER </s>
<s> A TEN BILLION DOLLAR STOCK SWAP WOULD COMBINE LOCKHEED AND MARTIN MARIETTA </s>
<s> DEFENSE DEPARTMENT OFFICIALS SAY THE PROPOSED MERGER RAISES SERIOUS ANTI TRUST QUESTIONS BUT THEY SAY THE COMBINATION OF THE COMPANIES COULD SAVE U. S. TAXPAYERS SOME MONEY </s>
<s> MORE FROM C. N. N.'S JAMIE MCINTYRE AT THE PENTAGON </s>
<s> MARTIN MARIETTA MAKES MOSTLY SPACE SYSTEMS SUCH AS THE TITAN ROCKET </s>
<s> LOCKHEED CONCENTRATES MORE ON AIRCRAFT INCLUDING THE NEXT GENERATION U. S. FIGHTER THE F. TWENTY TWO </s>
<s> THEIR PLANNED MERGER CREATES THE WORLD'S LARGEST SPACE AND DEFENSE COMPANY DESCRIBED BY COMPANY EXECUTIVES AS NEARLY A PERFECT MATCH </s>
<s> WE THINK THIS IS PRO COMPETITIVE AND WILL BENEFIT CUSTOMERS AND MAKE FOR A MORE ROBUST AND COMPETITIVE INDUSTRY </s>
<s> THE LOCKHEED MARTIN MARIETTA MERGER IS A DIRECT RESULT OF BIG CUTS IN PENTAGON WEAPONS PURCHASES AND THE MOVE TO BUY MORE TECHNOLOGY OFF THE SHELF </s>
<s> HARD PRESSED DEFENSE COMPANIES HAVE DOWN SIZED DIVERSIFIED AND CONSOLIDATED WITH OTHER COMPANIES </s>
<s> CONCEPTUALLY THAT MAKES GOOD SENSE </s>
<s> AS LONG AS WE CONTINUE TO HAVE COMPETITION ECONOMIES OF SCALE COULD HELP THE TAXPAYER IN THE LONG RUN </s>
<s> STILL A DEFENSE OFFICIAL SAYS THE LOCKHEED MARTIN DEAL RAISES SIGNIFICANT ANTI TRUST QUESTIONS AND A PENTAGON PANEL WILL REVIEW ITS IMPACT ON NATIONAL SECURITY </s>
<s> ONE CONCERN BOTH COMPANIES MAKE SPY SATELLITES AND TOGETHER COULD CORNER THE MARKET BUT SOME ANALYSTS SAY OVERALL THE NEW ALLIANCE MAY BE A PLUS FOR THE PENTAGON AND THE TAXPAYERS </s>
<s> IT COULD MAKE THINGS CHEAPER FOR THE DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE BECAUSE IF THESE COMPANIES CAN MERGE THEIR DIFFERENT CULTURES THEY SHOULD BE ABLE TO PRODUCE THINGS MORE CHEAPLY </s>
<s> IF THE PENTAGON IS TRULY WORRIED ABOUT NATIONAL SECURITY COMPANY EXECUTIVES SUGGEST IT SHOULD LOOK AT ITS OWN SHRINKING BUDGET </s>
<s> THIS TIME I THINK WE'RE IN DANGER OF CUTTING BACK ON MODERNIZATIONS TO THE POINT THAT WE COULD BUILD A HOLLOW FORCE AND I KNOW THE PEOPLE IN THE PENTAGON ARE MINDFUL OF THAT AND I HOPE WE CAN AVOID THAT TRAP </s>
<s> ONE DOWNSIDE IN THE SHORT TERM SOME JOBS WILL BE CUT </s>
<s> EVERYONE'S WORRIED IF THEIR JOB'S AT LOCKHEED </s>
<s> IT'S NEVER BEEN A SAFE PLACE TO WORK </s>
<s> YOU'VE NEVER KNOWN FOR SURE IF YOU'D HAVE A JOB TODAY OR TOMORROW </s>
<s> THE NEW LOCKHEED MARTIN WITH A WORK FORCE OF ONE HUNDRED SEVENTY THOUSAND AND REVENUES OF TWENTY THREE BILLION DOLLARS WILL DWARF ITS DEFENSE INDUSTRY COMPETITORS AND THAT GIVES IT ANOTHER BIG ADVANTAGE MORE CLOUT LOBBYING CONGRESS TO SAVE ITS PROGRAMS FROM THE PENTAGON'S BUDGET AXE </s>
<s> JAMIE MCINTYRE C. N. N. THE PENTAGON </s>
<s> A KEY DETECTIVE IN THE O. J. SIMPSON CASE HAS BEEN TAKEN OFF THE STREET AND REASSIGNED TO A DESK JOB BY THE LOS ANGELES POLICE DEPARTMENT </s>
<s> A SOURCE CLOSE TO THE CASE TELLS C. N. N. DETECTIVE MARK FUHRMAN WAS REASSIGNED BECAUSE HE IS NOW SO RECOGNIZABLE IT'S ALMOST IMPOSSIBLE FOR HIM TO WORK AS A DETECTIVE AT CRIME SCENES </s>
<s> THE SOURCE SAID THAT IT WAS JUST THAT FAME GOT IN THE WAY </s>
