<s> SIMPSON'S DEFENSE TEAM CONTENDS THAT FUHRMAN IS A RACIST AND IT HAS BEEN TRYING TO DISCREDIT HIS TESTIMONY </s>
<s> FUHRMAN'S ATTORNEY BLAMES DEFENSE TACTICS FOR FUHRMAN'S REASSIGNMENT </s>
<s> BOTH SIDES IN THE O. J. SIMPSON CASE ARE SCHEDULED BACK IN COURT WEDNESDAY </s>
<s> C. N. N. WILL HAVE LIVE COVERAGE BEGINNING AT TWELVE O'CLOCK NOON EASTERN NINE O'CLOCK PACIFIC </s>
<s> TOMORROW MAY REVEAL WHAT'S INSIDE A MYSTERY YELLOW ENVELOPE HELD BY THE COURT </s>
<s> IF IT IS A KNIFE AS SOME BELIEVE THEN THE MYSTERY WILL ONLY BECOME MORE COMPLICATED </s>
<s> C. N. N.'S MARC WATTS EXPLAINS WHY </s>
<s> THE DEFENDANT SHOULD BE HELD TO ANSWER FOR ALL OF THE CHARGES </s>
<s> THE DIFFICULT TASK FOR THE PROSECUTION IS TO CONVINCE A JURY THAT O. J. SIMPSON SINGLE HANDEDLY KILLED HIS EX WIFE NICOLE BROWN SIMPSON AND HER FRIEND RONALD GOLDMAN </s>
<s> IT'S THE PROSECUTION'S THEORY THAT IN THE COURSE OF ABOUT ONE HOUR SIMPSON STABS TO DEATH BOTH VICTIMS THEN DISPOSES OF BLOODY CLOTHING BLOODY SHOES AND POSSIBLY THE MURDER WEAPON </s>
<s> BECAUSE THEY HAVE NOT BEEN FOUND OR PRESENTED </s>
<s> THEN GOES BACK TO HIS HOUSE GETS CLEANED UP TO MEET THE LIMOUSINE DRIVER </s>
<s> AND THEN LEAVE A BLOODY GLOVE IN HIS BACKYARD </s>
<s> THAT JUST DOESN'T STAND UP TO LOGIC </s>
<s> IT'S A GERMAN MADE KNIFE </s>
<s> PROSECUTORS HAVE SUGGESTED A FIFTEEN INCH GERMAN MADE STILETTO KNIFE IS THE MURDER WEAPON </s>
<s> DURING THE PRELIMINARY HEARING AN EMPLOYEE OF AN L. A. CUTLERY STORE TESTIFIED SIMPSON BOUGHT A SIMILAR KNIFE AND ASKED FOR IT TO BE SHARPENED </s>
<s> SIMPSON IS A KNIFE COLLECTOR </s>
<s> YOU CAN SEE THE DIFFERENT TYPES OF DAGGERS </s>
<s> JIM ADVINCULA IS A KNIFE COLLECTOR ALSO </s>
<s> HE HAS MORE THAN ONE HUNDRED </s>
<s> COLLECTOR KNIVES AS A RULE ARE NOT SHARPENED </s>
<s> IN OTHER WORDS IF YOU SHARPEN THE KNIFE YOU'RE GOING TO USE IT </s>
<s> A RETIRED MARINE ADVINCULA TEACHES MARINES AT CAMP PENDLETON HAND TO HAND COMBAT AND HOW TO KILL WITH KNIVES </s>
<s> ADVINCULA SAYS THE ONLY KNIVES HE EVER SHARPENED WERE THE ONES HE FOUGHT WITH IN VIETNAM </s>
<s> DALE UPTON IS A KNIFE EXPERT ALSO WHO SAYS IT'S UNUSUAL FOR A COLLECTOR TO SHARPEN KNIVES </s>
<s> WITH A COLLECTOR'S ITEM THE MORE PRISTINE THE CONDITION THE MORE INCENTIVE FOR THE VALUE TO BE MAINTAINED OVER A PERIOD OF TIME </s>
<s> BUT DEFENSE SOURCES TELL C. N. N. THE FIFTEEN INCH STILETTO KNIFE IS INSIDE THE MYSTERIOUS ENVELOPE WITH A RECEIPT VERIFYING PURCHASE FROM ROSS CUTLERY STORE </s>
<s> DEFENSE EXPERTS WHO'VE EXAMINED THE KNIFE SAY IT'S IN MINT CONDITION AND HAS NOTHING OF AN INCRIMINATING NATURE ABOUT IT </s>
<s> IF SO THAT MIGHT DESTROY THE PROSECUTION'S THEORY SIMPSON USED THE STILETTO IN THE KILLINGS </s>
<s> FURTHER DOUBT WAS RAISED DURING THE PRELIMINARY HEARING BY TESTIMONY FROM THE DEPUTY MEDICAL EXAMINER </s>
<s> IRWIN GOLDEN SAID THERE WERE TWO DIFFERENT TYPES OF KNIFE WOUNDS </s>
<s> SOME WERE SMOOTH AND SOME WERE JAGGED </s>
<s> A CLEAR INFERENCE THAT THERE MAY BE MORE THAN ONE KILLER </s>
<s> BUT MEDICAL EXAMINERS SAY TWO DIFFERENT TYPES OF KNIFE WOUNDS DON'T NECESSARILY MEAN TWO KNIVES OR TWO KILLERS </s>
<s> IN WASHINGTON D. C. MURDER CAPITAL OF THE UNITED STATES CHIEF MEDICAL EXAMINER JOYCE CARTER HAS SEEN HER SHARE OF STABBING VICTIMS AND AUTOPSIES </s>
<s> SHE SAYS A SMOOTH EDGED KNIFE LIKE A STILETTO CAN CAUSE A JAGGED WOUND IF THE VICTIM IS MOVING OR RESISTING </s>
<s> OR IT MIGHT BE THAT IN THE PERPETRATOR THAT IS USING THAT WEAPON MAY TWIST THE WEAPON MAKING THAT WOUND LOOK JAGGED </s>
<s> HERE'S A CLASSIC EXAMPLE HE STABS ME RIGHT OVER HERE AND I PUSH RIGHT OVER HERE </s>
<s> THIS IS NOW GOING TO WHAT </s>
<s> IT MAKES A IT MAKES A HOOK SO IT CAN HAVE THE ILLUSION OF WHAT </s>
<s> BEING A TWO DIFFERENT TYPES OF KNIVES </s>
<s> THIS IS A CASE THAT EVERYBODY HAS JUMPED TO AN IMMEDIATE AND UNREALISTIC CONCLUSION </s>
<s> THERE ARE NUMEROUS THEORIES ABOUT WHO COMMITTED THE KILLINGS </s>
<s> IF IT WAS A PROFESSIONAL IT WOULD HAVE BEEN A MINIMUM OF NUMBER OF HITS </s>
<s> IN OTHER WORDS MAYBE ACROSS THE JUGULAR VEIN MAYBE INTO THE HEART OR A GOOD ONE ACROSS THE STOMACH </s>
<s> IN ALL BOTH VICTIMS WERE STABBED NEARLY TWENTY TIMES IN A MYSTERIOUS CASE NOT ONLY OF WHO DID IT BUT WITH KIND OF KNIFE </s>
