<s> HERE NOW A LOOK AT THE MAN </s>
<s> THERE IS NO CUBAN LAW THAT SAYS FIDEL CASTRO CAN SERVE BUT ONE TERM </s>
<s> THIS MAN IS CUBA'S PRESIDENT IN PERPETUITY </s>
<s> SINCE NINETEEN FIFTY NINE WHEN HIS FORCES OVERTHREW THE BATTISTA REGIME THIS SON OF A WEALTHY SUGAR PLANTATION OWNER IN ORRIENTE PROVINCE HAS BEEN EL COMANDANTE </s>
<s> IN THE BEGINNING HIS REVOLUTION WAS SWORN TO WIPING OUT CORRUPTION CLASS AND RACIAL DIVISIONS POVERTY AND CRADLE TO THE GRAVE EXPLOITATION OF THE MASSES </s>
<s> THE FLAMES OF CASTRO'S FURIOUS CONTEMPT FOR WASHINGTON'S POLICIES WERE FED BY UNITED STATES DOMINATION OF HIS ISLAND BEFORE THE TURN OF THE CENTURY SYMBOLIZED BY ONE BUSINESS IN PARTICULAR THE UNITED FRUIT COMPANY WHOSE SUGAR OPERATIONS OWNED LAND AND THE PEASANTS ON IT </s>
<s> IN THE BEGINNING CASTRO A PASSIONATE STUDENT OF HISTORY READ THOMAS JEFFERSON CLOSELY </s>
<s> ONCE HE WROTE PRESIDENT ROOSEVELT CONGRATULATING HIM ON HIS NINETEEN FORTY RE ELECTION TRIUMPH </s>
<s> CASTRO'S NINETEEN FIFTY NINE MEETING WITH VICE PRESIDENT RICHARD NIXON WAS ANYTHING BUT </s>
<s> NIXON SENSING COMMUNIST LEANINGS SOUNDED ALARMS WARNING OF DANGER TO AMERICAN INTERESTS </s>
<s> THE BUDDING SOVIET CONNECTION SYMBOLIZED BY CASTRO'S NEW YORK MEETING WITH NIKITA KHRUSCHEV WAS NIXON'S CONFIRMATION </s>
<s> WASHINGTON MADE PLANS </s>
<s> THEN CAME THE NINETEEN SIXTY ONE BAY OF PIGS ATTEMPT TO OVERTHROW CASTRO </s>
<s> HATCHED IN THE EISENHOWER ADMINISTRATION AND EXECUTED UNDER KENNEDY CASTRO PREVAILED </s>
<s> KENNEDY TOOK THE BLAME </s>
<s> THE FOLLOWING YEAR AFTER AMERICAN AERIAL SURVEILLANCE DETECTED SOVIET MISSILES ON CUBAN SOIL THE WORLD WAS SNATCHED FROM THE BRINK OF NUCLEAR WAR WHEN MOSCOW CAUGHT RED HANDED BACKED DOWN AND WITHDREW THE MISSILES </s>
<s> FROM THE SOVIET UNION CUBA WAS RECEIVING OIL BILLIONS OF RUBLES AS WELL AS WEAPONS AND TRAINING </s>
<s> CASTRO WOULD GO ON TO RIDE A ROLLER COASTER OF ADULATION FROM THIRD WORLD COUNTRIES </s>
<s> HE PROJECTED HIMSELF AND HIS TROOPS GLOBALLY IN ANGOLA AND ETHIOPIA </s>
<s> CASTRO CONTINUALLY SOLIDIFIED HIS POWER REPRESSING ANY DISSENT WHILE INSTITUTING ECONOMIC EDUCATIONAL AND HEALTH REFORMS IN THE FACE OF FAILURES SETBACKS AND RATIONING ONCE MOSCOW'S BILLIONS WERE WITHDRAWN </s>
<s> THE NINETEEN EIGHTY MARIEL BOAT LIFT TOLD THE WORLD CONVINCINGLY THAT LIFE IN CUBA WAS NOT PARADISE </s>
<s> ONE HUNDRED AND TWENTY FIVE THOUSAND CUBANS GAVE TESTIMONY BY LEAVING INCLUDING SOME UNDESIRABLES ADDED BY THE GOVERNMENT FOR GOOD MEASURE </s>
<s> FIDEL CASTRO HAS OUTLASTED EIGHT UNITED STATES PRESIDENTS AND NOW IT'S BILL CLINTON'S TURN </s>
<s> LET ME BE CLEAR THE CUBAN GOVERNMENT WILL NOT SUCCEED IN ANY ATTEMPT TO DICTATE AMERICAN IMMIGRATION POLICY </s>
<s> THEY PRESSURE CLINTON AND CLINTON GIVES IN TO PRESSURES FROM THE ULTRA RIGHT GENERALLY FROM THIS MAFIA AND HE DECIDES TO ADOPT A NUMBER OF DRASTIC MEASURES </s>
<s> THE SLOGANS HAVE CHANGED FROM COMMUNISM ALMIGHTY TO SOCIALISM OR DEATH </s>
<s> CASTRO HAS DEMANDED RESPECT AND A CUBA FREE OF A U. S. ECONOMIC BLOCKADE </s>
<s> IF HE CANNOT GET THAT HE IS DETERMINED TO GET WASHINGTON'S ATTENTION ON THE IMMIGRATION ISSUE BY LETTING HIS PEOPLE GO ON RAFTS </s>
<s> ANOTHER CONFRONTATION AND CASTRO IS HOPING ANOTHER OPPORTUNITY TO TALK ABOUT EVERYTHING </s>
<s> AND JUST TO REMIND YOU OUR VIEWERS AROUND THE WORLD THERE ARE MORE ISSUES THAN JUST IMMIGRATION ISSUES SEPARATING THE UNITED STATES IN WASHINGTON </s>
<s> VERY BRIEFLY JUST TO FILL YOU IN ONE MAJOR CLAIM THE UNITED STATES HAS AGAINST THIS GOVERNMENT AND THIS ISLAND REPUBLIC IS THAT U. S. COMPANIES AND CITIZENS LOST BILLIONS OF DOLLARS WHEN CUBA EXPROPRIATED PROPERTY </s>
<s> THE BILLIONS INCLUDE HUNDREDS OF MILLIONS OF DOLLARS IF YOU INCLUDE ACCRUED INTEREST NOW </s>
<s> ALSO THE UNITED STATES HAS BEEN CONCERNED ABOUT HUMAN RIGHTS HERE IN CUBA </s>
<s> PRESIDENT CLINTON ALLUDED TO THAT WHEN NEARLY TWO WEEKS AGO HE ANNOUNCED HIS FOUR POINT CRACK DOWN PROGRAM AND SAID THAT THE UNITED STATES WOULD GO TO THE UNITED NATIONS TO GET A U. N. RESOLUTION ON HUMAN RIGHTS ALLEGED VIOLATIONS HERE </s>
<s> CUBA HAS VERY STRONG CONTENTIONS AGAINST THE UNITED STATES INCLUDING THE RADIO MARTI BROADCAST FROM THE UNITED STATES AIMED AT THIS ISLAND THE UNILATERAL UNITED STATES ECONOMIC EMBARGO WHICH FIDEL CASTRO HAS RAILED AGAINST CONTINUALLY AND LASTLY AND MOST EMOTIONALLY THAT GUANTANAMO NAVAL BASE AT THE SOUTHEASTERN END OF THIS ISLAND </s>
