<s> AND THESE RAFTERS SAY ONCE THEY CLEAR THE TWELVE MILE LIMIT ONCE THEY GET OUT THERE IN INTERNATIONAL WATERS WHEREVER THEY REACH LAND FALL THEY'RE GOING TO RELEASE THAT CARRIER PIGEON AND THEY'RE HOPING THAT THE PIGEON WILL COME BACK HOME TO CUBA TO TELL THEIR FRIENDS FROM WHATEVER NEIGHBORHOOD THEY LEFT HOW THEY FARED </s>
