<s> C. N. N.'S TONY CLARK INTERFACES AT THE HIGH TECH CAFE </s>
<s> AT INFOMART DALLAS'S COMPUTER MARKETPLACE TECHNOLOGY IS MORE THAN A TRENDY COME ON TO CUSTOMERS </s>
<s> HERE AT THE RESTAURANT THE SPECIALTY IS THE LAPTOP LUNCH </s>
<s> CUSTOMERS BRING THEIR LAPTOPS TO LUNCH SO THEY CAN WORK WHILE THEY DINE ON COMPUTER ORIENTED CUISINE </s>
<s> IF YOU NEED TO SEND A FAX YOU CAN SEND A FAX </s>
<s> IF YOU NEED TO LOOK UP A TELEPHONE NUMBER IN YOUR ACCOUNT MANAGEMENT FILE YOU CAN DO THAT </s>
<s> SO IT'S JUST MUCH MORE EFFICIENT THAN CARRYING AROUND NOTEBOOKS AND REAMS OF PAPER </s>
<s> THE RECENTLY RENOVATED HIGH TECH CAFE IS DECORATED WITH TECHNOLOGICAL TIDBITS </s>
<s> THERE ARE FERNS MADE FROM OUT OF DATE CIRCUIT BOARDS VASES FILL WITH USED KEYBOARD KEYS COLUMNS THAT LOOK LIKE COAXIAL CABLES AND A MAITRE D. STAND MADE FROM A NINETEEN SIXTIES VINTAGE UNIVAC COMPUTER </s>
