<s> THERE ARE PHONE JACKS AND ELECTRICAL OUTLETS NEXT TO THE TABLES SO CUSTOMERS CAN STAY ELECTRONICALLY HOOKED TO THEIR HOME OFFICE </s>
<s> IT ALLOWS YOU TO EAT AND YOU CAN DO THE THINGS YOU NEED TO DO DOWN HERE AT LUNCH WITHOUT MISSING A BEAT UP IN THE OFFICE </s>
