<s> IN ITSELF IT'S NOT SIGNIFICANT BUT WHEN YOU COUPLE THAT WITH SOME OF THE OTHER SETBACKS OF THE ADMINISTRATION THE DIFFICULTIES IN FOREIGN POLICY AND SOME OF THE OTHER PERSONAL PROBLEMS HE'S HAD IT'S JUST ANOTHER STRAW THAT IS SLOWLY BUT SURELY BREAKING THE CAMEL'S BACK </s>
