<s> HE SAYS USE OF CAMPAIGN FUNDS IS NOT HIS PRIMARY CONCERN BUT HE DOES THINK THAT RATHER THAN LOOKING FOR NEW AREAS TO REGULATE THE F. E. C. SHOULD BE DOING A BETTER JOB WITH WHAT'S ALREADY ON IT'S PLATE </s>
