<s> FROM NEW YORK NPR'S MELISSA BLOCK REPORTS </s>
<s> THE UNION OF LOCKHEED AND MARTIN MARIETTA CREATES A HUGE ARSENAL OF MILITARY AND AEROSPACE TECHNOLOGY </s>
<s> LOCKHEED BUILDS THE F. ONE HUNDRED SEVENTEEN STEALTH FIGHTER AS WELL AS THE F. TWENTY TWO AND F. SIXTEEN FIGHTER JETS THE HERCULES C. ONE HUNDRED THIRTY CARGO PLANE AND THE TRIDENT SUBMARINE LAUNCHED BALLISTIC MISSILE </s>
