<s> GLOBAL EXCHANGE </s>
<s> I THINK THERE IS SOMETHING IN THE U. S. PEOPLE THAT REALLY WANTS TO BE PART OF A GLOBAL VILLAGE REALLY WANTS TO FEEL CONNECTED TO THE REST OF THE WORLD </s>
<s> THE INDIVIDUAL PEOPLE CAN MAKE HUGE POLICY DIFFERENCES WHEN THEY'RE IN THE RIGHT PLACE AT THE RIGHT TIME </s>
<s> GLOBAL EXCHANGE AND CITIZEN TO CITIZEN DIPLOMACY ON THIS EDITION OF COMMON GROUND </s>
<s> COMMON GROUND IS A PROGRAM ON WORLD AFFAIRS AND THE PEOPLE WHO SHAPE EVENTS </s>
<s> IT'S PRODUCED BY THE STANLEY FOUNDATION </s>
<s> I'M KEITH PORTER </s>
<s> FOR OVER SIX YEARS A NON PROFIT GROUP CALLED GLOBAL EXCHANGE HAS HELPED BUILD BRIDGES BETWEEN GRASS ROOTS MOVEMENTS IN THE U. S. AND THE SO CALLED THIRD WORLD </s>
<s> ONE WAY THEY DO THIS IS BY TAKING AMERICANS TO SOME OF THE WORLD'S LESS VISITED LOCALES </s>
<s> MEDEA BENJAMIN CO DIRECTOR OF GLOBAL EXCHANGE CALLS THESE TRIPS REALITY TOURS </s>
<s> WE GO TO ABOUT TWELVE DIFFERENT COUNTRIES INCLUDING SOUTH AFRICA SENEGAL IN WEST AFRICA </s>
<s> WE'VE TAKEN GROUPS TO INDIA TO BRAZIL CENTRAL AMERICA </s>
<s> CUBA IS THE PLACE WE GO THE MOST </s>
<s> WE TAKE ABOUT EIGHTEEN TRIPS A YEAR TO CUBA ALONE </s>
<s> WE TAKE GROUPS TO CENTRAL AMERICA TO MEXICO TO VIETNAM AND CAMBODIA </s>
<s> SO THAT'S ONE OF OUR PROGRAMS THE REALITY TOURS </s>
<s> AND THEN SEPARATE FROM THAT WE HAVE A FAIR TRADE PROGRAM WHERE WE BUY CRAFTS FROM TWENTY TWO COUNTRIES AND WE SELL THEM IN OUR STORES </s>
<s> RIGHT NOW WE HAVE TWO </s>
<s> WE'RE OPENING A THIRD IN ABOUT A MONTH </s>
<s> AND WE HOPE YOU KNOW ONE DAY TO HAVE STORES ALL OVER THE COUNTRY THAT WOULD BE NOT ONLY STORES FOR SELLING THIRD WORLD CRAFTS AT A PRICE THAT'S GOOD FOR THE PRODUCERS BUT ALSO WOULD BE CENTERS FOR EDUCATION ON GLOBAL ISSUES </s>
<s> THAT SOUNDS INTERESTING </s>
<s> SO WE'VE GOT REALITY TOURS </s>
<s> WE HAVE THE CRAFT ITEMS AND THEN WHAT ARE THE ELEMENTS </s>
<s> WELL THEN WE HAVE OUR PUBLIC EDUCATION DEPARTMENT </s>
<s> THERE WE PUT OUT OUR OWN BOOKS AND OTHER EDUCATIONAL MATERIALS AND THOSE WILL BE ON ISSUES AFFECTING THE UNITED STATES FOREIGN POLICY MOST OF THE TIMES </s>
<s> SO WE DO A LOT OF WORK AROUND U. S. POLICY TOWARDS SOUTH AFRICA OR U. S. POLICY TOWARDS CUBA OR VIETNAM </s>
<s> WE PUBLISH BOOKS ABOUT HOW PEOPLE CAN GET INVOLVED AND GO VOLUNTEER IN THESE COUNTRIES </s>
<s> SO WE HAVE A BOOK CALLED ALTERNATIVES TO THE PEACE CORPS THAT GIVE PEOPLE ONE HUNDRED TWENTY DIFFERENT ORGANIZATIONS THAT SEND VOLUNTEERS OVERSEAS </s>
<s> WE HAVE ANOTHER BOOK CALLED BRIDGING THE GLOBAL GAP THAT GIVES PEOPLE IDEAS OF HOW THEY CAN GET INVOLVED IN HUMAN RIGHTS WORK OR ENVIRONMENTAL WORK SO THAT'S OUR PUBLIC EDUCATION DEPARTMENT </s>
<s> AND PART OF THAT WHAT WE ALSO DO IS WE BRING COMMUNITY ACTIVISTS FROM ALL OVER THE WORLD TO COME TO THE UNITED STATES AND DO SPEAKING TOURS MOSTLY ON COLLEGE CAMPUSES CHURCH GROUPS COMMUNITY CENTERS AND TALK ABOUT ISSUES THAT ARE SORT OF THE BURNING ISSUES OF THE DAY </s>
<s> NOW I WANT TO ASK MORE ABOUT THE REALITY TOURS BECAUSE I THINK PEOPLE ARE REALLY INTERESTED IN THIS </s>
<s> NOW THESE AREN'T VACATIONS WOULD YOU CALL THEM </s>
<s> WELL THEY'RE VACATIONS IN THAT IT'S A BREAK FROM YOUR USUAL WORK AND ALSO I MEAN YOU'VE BEEN ON ONE OF THEM WE'VE WE USUALLY HAVE A GREAT DEAL OF FUN WHILE WE LEARN AT THE SAME TIME </s>
