<s> WELL WE DIDN'T TALK ABOUT WHAT THEY DO WHEN THEY'RE THERE SO MAYBE I SHOULD </s>
<s> O. K. </s>
<s> SHOULD SAY THAT SOME OF THE THINGS THEY DO IS MEET WITH LEADERS OF DIFFERENT COUNTRIES AND YOU KNOW SOMETIMES IT'LL BE ON A HIGH LEVEL ALTHOUGH THAT'S NOT REALLY OUR INTEREST </s>
<s> OUR REAL INTEREST IS TO MEET WITH ORDINARY PEOPLE IN DIFFERENT WALKS OF LIFE </s>
<s> SO IF WE GO TO VIETNAM WE'LL GO OUT TO THE COUNTRYSIDE AND MEET WITH FARMERS OR WE'LL GO AND MEET WITH HEALTH WORKERS </s>
