<s> IT'S REALLY ORDINARY PEOPLE MEETING WITH ORDINARY PEOPLE AND LEARNING ABOUT WHAT THEIR LIVES ARE LIKE AND LEARNING FROM EACH OTHER </s>
<s> AND IT'S QUITE AMAZING WE HAVE PEOPLE WHO COME BACK FROM OUR TRIPS WHO ARE SO TRANSFORMED IN THEIR OWN WAY OF THINKING THAT THEY DECIDE TO TRANSFORM THEIR OWN WAY OF LIVING HERE IN THE UNITED STATES </s>
