<s> WELL SINCE WE'RE TALKING ABOUT CUBA THE FREEDOM TO TRAVEL CAMPAIGN RECEIVED AN AWFUL LOT OF PUBLICITY EARLY THIS YEAR </s>
<s> TELL US WHAT HAPPENED WHAT THE GOALS WERE AND HOW IT ALL TURNED OUT </s>
<s> WELL WE WERE TALKING ABOUT GLOBAL EXCHANGE AND OUR REALITY TOURS </s>
<s> AND WE'VE TAKEN GROUPS TO SO MANY DIFFERENT COUNTRIES AND NEVER RUN ACROSS U. S. RESTRICTIONS </s>
<s> WE TAKE GROUPS TO CHINA </s>
