<s> AND WE KIND OF SCRATCHED OUR HEADS AFTER AWHILE AND SAID WELL WAIT THIS DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE </s>
<s> YOU KNOW EVEN AT THE HEIGHT OF THE COLD WAR YOU COULD GO TO THE SOVIET UNION AND EASTERN EUROPE </s>
