<s> HOW DID YOU FIND OUT </s>
<s> I MEAN DID YOU GO DOWN THERE AND TRY TO GET SOME MONEY AND THEY SAID SORRY OR WHAT HAPPENED </s>
<s> WELL THAT'S ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED </s>
<s> WE WENT DOWN THERE AND WE TRIED TO CASH A CHECK </s>
<s> THEY SAID NO THAT THE U. S. GOVERNMENT HAS FROZEN YOUR ACCOUNT AND YOU CAN ONLY PUT MONEY IN YOU CAN'T TAKE MONEY OUT. WE SAID OH NOW THAT'S NICE OF THEM </s>
<s> WE WERE IN TOTAL SHOCK BECAUSE WE HAD NEVER GOTTEN A LETTER FROM THE GOVERNMENT WARNING US THAT WE SHOULDN'T DO THE TRIP </s>
<s> THERE IS WHAT'S CALLED A CEASE AND DESIST ORDER THAT OTHER GROUPS HAVE GOTTEN WHEN THEY'VE TRIED TO TAKE GROUPS TO CUBA </s>
<s> WE NEVER GOT THAT KIND OF CEASE AND DESIST LETTER </s>
<s> NOTHING YOU KNOW </s>
<s> THAT WAS THE FIRST INKLING WE HAD THAT THE GOVERNMENT PLANNED TO DO ANYTHING TO STOP THE TRIP </s>
<s> AND REALLY I THINK IT BACKFIRED ON THE GOVERNMENT BECAUSE AS YOU SAID WE GOT TREMENDOUS PRESS FROM THE FACT THAT YOU KNOW HERE IS THIS NICE EDUCATIONAL GROUP OF PEOPLE THAT WANT TO GO TO CUBA TO LEARN ABOUT CUBA JUST LIKE THEY WANT TO GO TO ANY OTHER COUNTRY TO LEARN ABOUT THAT COUNTRY AND THE U. S. GOVERNMENT FREEZES THEIR BANK ACCOUNT </s>
<s> IT DOESN'T LOOK GOOD YOU KNOW </s>
<s> IT DOESN'T LOOK LIKE A DEMOCRATIC SYSTEM </s>
<s> SO WE GOT A LOT OF PRESS AND I WOULD SAY ONE HUNDRED PERCENT IN OUR FAVOR BECAUSE WE'RE NOT SAYING WE'RE DOING THIS TO SUPPORT SOCIALISM TO SUPPORT FIDEL CASTRO YOU KNOW </s>
<s> IT'S NOTHING LIKE THAT </s>
<s> WE'RE JUST SAYING WE FEEL WE HAVE THE RIGHT AS U. S. CITIZENS TO GO PLACES AND LEARN FOR OURSELVES </s>
<s> SO IT BACKFIRED IN THE SENSE THAT WE GOT A LOT MORE SUPPORT </s>
<s> WE GOT CONGRESSPEOPLE WRITING LETTERS </s>
<s> WE DID A PRESS CONFERENCE IN WASHINGTON </s>
<s> WE EVEN HAD CONGRESSPEOPLE COMING TO THE PRESS CONFERENCE TO SAY U. S. PRESIDENTS SHOULDN'T RESTRICT TRAVEL AND WE MANAGED TO GET THE U. S. CONGRESS TO PASS A NON BINDING RESOLUTION SAYING PRESIDENTS SHOULDN'T RESTRICT TRAVEL TO ANY COUNTRY FOR EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES </s>
<s> SO WE FEEL THE MOMENTUM IS ON OUR SIDE BUT RIGHT NOW OUR ACCOUNTS ARE STILL FROZEN AND WE'RE PUSHING AHEAD </s>
<s> WE HAVE ANOTHER TRIP PLANNED FOR OCTOBER AS THE THIRD FREEDOM TO TRAVEL TRIP </s>
<s> NOW YOU SAY THE ACCOUNT'S STILL FROZEN BUT YOU WENT ON THE TRIP </s>
<s> HOW WERE YOU ABLE TO DO THAT IF THE MONEY WASN'T THERE </s>
<s> WELL THAT WAS ANOTHER AMAZING THING THAT HAPPENED </s>
<s> ALL THE PRESS THAT WE GOT WHEN PEOPLE HEARD ABOUT IT THEY CALLED US FROM ALL OVER THE COUNTRY </s>
<s> THEY ONLY KNEW THAT WE WERE IN SAN FRANCISCO </s>
<s> THEY HAD HEARD MAYBE THE WORLD GLOBAL EXCHANGE AND THEY FOUND US IN THE PHONE BOOK AND THEY CALLED FROM LITERALLY ALL OVER THE COUNTRY AND SAID I THINK THIS IS TERRIBLE </s>
<s> GOVERNMENTS SHOULDN'T STOP PEOPLE FROM LEARNING AND I WANT TO HELP YOU OUT </s>
<s> THERE WERE DONATIONS MOSTLY OF LIKE TWENTY FIVE DOLLARS FIFTY DOLLARS </s>
<s> SOME PEOPLE SENT IN QUITE SIZABLE DONATIONS </s>
<s> AND THEY COULDN'T SEND IT IN IN A CHECK TOO </s>
<s> WE HAD TO DO IT IN OTHER KINDS OF WAYS BECAUSE WE HAD NO ACCOUNT </s>
<s> SO IT AMAZING THE KIND OF GRASS ROOTS SUPPORT WE GOT AND THAT WE MANAGED IN ONE WEEK TO EITHER HAVE DONATED TO US OR ON LOAN TO US THE FORTY THREE THOUSAND DOLLARS THAT WE NEEDED TO COMPLETE THE TRIP </s>
<s> WE'RE TALKING IN THIS EDITION OF COMMON GROUND WITH MEDEA BENJAMIN CO DIRECTOR OF THE SAN FRANCISCO BASED GLOBAL EXCHANGE </s>
<s> PRINTED TRANSCRIPTS AND AUDIO CASSETTES OF THIS PROGRAM ARE AVAILABLE </s>
<s> LISTEN AT THE END OF THE BROADCAST FOR DETAILS </s>
<s> COMMON GROUND IS A SERVICE OF THE STANLEY FOUNDATION A NON PROFIT NON PARTISAN ORGANIZATION THAT CONDUCTS A WIDE RANGE OF PROGRAMS MEANT TO PROVOKE THOUGHT AND ENCOURAGE DIALOGUE ON WORLD AFFAIRS </s>
<s> MEDEA BENJAMIN HAS BEEN DESCRIBING THE FREEDOM TO TRAVEL CAMPAIGN'S LATEST CUBA TRIP </s>
<s> WHEN THE GROUP RETURNED FROM CUBA LAST YEAR MANY OF THEM WERE DETAINED AND SOME HAD THEIR PASSPORTS SEIZED </s>
<s> I ASKED BENJAMIN IF THIS YEAR'S GROUP GOT THE SAME TREATMENT </s>
<s> NO IT WAS A VERY DIFFERENT RECEPTION WE GOT THIS TIME </s>
<s> MOST OF US CAME THROUGH HOUSTON AND WHEN WE CAME BACK INTO THE COUNTRY ON THE FIRST TIME THERE WERE SPECIAL SECURITY AGENTS ALL OVER THE PLACE </s>
<s> YOU COULD SEE THEM </s>
<s> IT WAS LIKE WE WERE SOME BIG DRUG DEALERS WHO'D JUST COME INTO THE COUNTRY YOU KNOW </s>
<s> THIS TIME IT WAS VERY QUIET AND IN FACT WHEN WE CAME THROUGH WE HEARD THEM SAY OH HERE THESE ARE PEOPLE FROM CUBA BE NICE TO THEM </s>
<s> SO THEY WERE VERY NICE TO MOST OF US </s>
<s> THEY HASSLED A COUPLE OF PEOPLE PRETTY ARBITRARILY </s>
<s> IN FACT MY OWN DAUGHTER WHO IS THIRTEEN YEARS OLD AND WAS ON THE TRIP HAD A PRETTY TRAUMATIC EXPERIENCE </s>
<s> SHE HAD A T. SHIRT THAT SAID CUBA ON IT THAT IRONICALLY HAD BEEN MADE IN CHINA BUT THE CUSTOMS AGENT THOUGHT THAT THAT SHOULD BE SEIZED AND WANTED HER TO TAKE OFF HER SHIRT </s>
<s> AND YOU KNOW IT'S PRETTY TRAUMATIC FOR THIRTEEN YEAR OLD GIRLS TO BE TOLD TO TAKE OFF THEIR SHIRT </s>
<s> AND SHE STARTED CRYING AND IT MADE A WHOLE SCENE </s>
<s> AND THAT PICTURE GOT INTO A BUNCH OF PAPERS AND THEY FINALLY LET HER GO </s>
<s> THEY ASKED HER TO MAIL THE SHIRT </s>
<s> BUT FOR THE MOST PART I WOULD SAY THAT WE FELT LIKE OUR TREATMENT WAS PRETTY GOOD AND THAT IT WAS AN INDICATION TO US THAT THE TIDE IS TURNING AND THAT THE U. S. GOVERNMENT IS GOING TO CHANGE ITS POSITION ON THIS </s>
<s> WELL IT SEEMS LIKE ALMOST EVERY MAJOR NEWSPAPER IN THE COUNTRY HAS WRITTEN AN EDITORIAL CALLING FOR SOME DEGREE OF CHANGE IN U. S. POLICY TOWARD CUBA </s>
<s> SOME NEWSPAPERS CALLING FOR A TOTAL LIFTING OF THE EMBARGO SOME SAYING MAYBE WE SHOULD LIFT THE PRESS BAN SOME SAYING MAYBE THE TRAVEL BAN </s>
<s> DO YOU SEE ANY POTENTIAL FOR CHANGE </s>
<s> WELL I THINK IT'S GOT TO CHANGE </s>
<s> IT'S JUST A QUESTION OF HOW QUICKLY </s>
<s> OUR ISSUE THE ONE ON TRAVEL IS THE EASIEST ONE FOR THE PRESIDENT TO CHANGE BECAUSE ALL HE'S GOT TO DO IS GIVE HIS O. K. TO CHANGE THE REGULATIONS </s>
<s> IT DOESN'T HAVE TO GO THROUGH CONGRESS THERE DOESN'T HAVE TO BE ANY LAW AND IT'S ALSO A CONSTITUTIONAL ISSUE ABOUT OUR RIGHT TO TRAVEL </s>
<s> SO HE DOESN'T HAVE TO COME OFF AS BEING SOFT ON CUBA </s>
<s> NOW I THINK THE WHOLE EMBARGO'S GOT TO BE LIFTED AND IT'S AN ABSOLUTELY HORRENDOUS POLICY THAT'S BEEN SO COUNTERPRODUCTIVE SO IRRATIONAL SO DESTRUCTIVE THAT I THINK THE ENTIRE EMBARGO'S GOT TO BE LIFTED </s>
<s> BUT I DON'T THINK CLINTON HAS THE UMPH LET'S SAY TO DO IT RIGHT NOW </s>
<s> PERHAPS IF HE'S ELECTED TO A SECOND TERM OR IRONICALLY IF WE GET A REPUBLICAN PRESIDENT IT'LL PROBABLY BE EASIER FOR A REPUBLICAN TO DO </s>
<s> SO THE EMBARGO'S GOT TO BE LIFTED IN THE NEXT COUPLE OF YEARS BUT I THINK THESE TRAVEL RESTRICTIONS COULD BE LIFTED MUCH SOONER </s>
<s> WHEN YOU WERE IN CUBA WHAT DO THE CUBANS SAY ABOUT THE TRAVEL RESTRICTION AND ABOUT THE EMBARGO </s>
<s> WELL IT DEPENDS WHO YOU TALK TO </s>
<s> BUT IT'S INTERESTING THAT EVEN CUBANS WHO DON'T SUPPORT THEIR GOVERNMENT AND WOULD LIKE TO SEE FIDEL CASTRO OUT OF POWER MOST OF THEM THANK US FOR WHAT WE'RE DOING AND SAY THAT THEY THINK THAT OPEN DIALOGUE AND COMMUNICATION IS A POSITIVE THING </s>
<s> SO YOU GET PEOPLE ON BOTH SIDES OF THE POLITICAL SPECTRUM IN CUBA CALLING FOR MORE U. S. VISITORS TO COME AND MORE U. S. BUSINESS TO COME </s>
<s> YOU KNOW IT IS SUCH A LOGICAL POSITION TO SAY THAT IF YOU WANT TO SEE THE FALL OF SOCIALISM IF YOU WANT TO SEE AN END TO FIDEL CASTRO FLOOD THEM WITH U. S. TOURISTS AND FLOOD THEM WITH U. S. BUSINESSES </s>
<s> SO ALLIANCES CAN BE MADE AMONG PEOPLE WHO THINK THAT THERE ARE VERY GOOD THINGS IN CUBA'S SOCIALIST SYSTEM THAT THEY WANT TO SEE SAVED LIKE THE GOOD HEALTH CARE SYSTEM THE GOOD EDUCATION SYSTEM </s>
<s> AND LET'S TRY NOT TO STRANGLE THEM AND LET'S NOT USE FOOD AND MEDICINES AS A WEAPON LIKE WE'RE DOING NOW I MEAN THAT WE CAN'T EVEN SELL FOOD OR MEDICINES TO CUBA I THINK IS PRETTY CRIMINAL </s>
<s> SO THERE'S ALLIANCES THAT COULD BE MADE WITH DIFFERENT TYPES OF PEOPLE PEOPLE FROM THE HUMANITARIAN COMMUNITY THE SOCIAL JUSTICE COMMUNITY WITH PEOPLE FROM THE BUSINESS COMMUNITY TO LIFT THE EMBARGO </s>
<s> THIS INTERVIEW WITH MEDEA BENJAMIN WAS CONDUCTED JUST BEFORE THE RECENT CHANGES IN U. S. POLICY TOWARD CUBA </s>
<s> DESPITE THE CHANGES A SPOKESMAN FOR GLOBAL EXCHANGE TOLD ME THEY WILL DO ALL THEY CAN TO CONTINUE THE FREEDOM TO TRAVEL CAMPAIGN AND THEIR REALITY TOURS TO CUBA </s>
<s> I WANT TO MOVE INTO ANOTHER AREA BECAUSE YOU WERE IN CHIAPAS EARLIER THIS YEAR </s>
<s> TELL US WHY YOU WERE THERE AND WHAT YOU FOUND </s>
<s> WELL I WAS IN CHIAPAS ON JANUARY SIXTH </s>
<s> I WENT WITH THE FIRST HUMAN RIGHTS DELEGATION TO REACH CHIAPAS AFTER THE ZAPPATISTA EZLN UPRISING ON JANUARY FIRST </s>
<s> I WENT BECAUSE I WAS WATCHING TELEVISION ONE NIGHT AND SAW SOME VERY HORRENDOUS SCENES ON THE T. V. OF THESE INDIGENOUS PEOPLE WITH FAKE GUNS WITH WOODEN GUNS BLEEDING IN THE MIDDLE OF THE STREET AND BEING LEFT FOR SEVERAL DAYS TO BLEED TO DEATH BECAUSE THE MEXICAN GOVERNMENT WOULDN'T LET ANY RED CROSS PEOPLE OR ANYBODY IN THERE TO TAKE THE WOUNDED </s>
<s> AND IT JUST YOU KNOW TUGGED AT MY HEART STRINGS </s>
<s> I COULDN'T WATCH IT AND NOT DO SOMETHING AND I CALLED MEXICO AND I SAID I REALLY WANT TO GET DOWN THERE </s>
<s> I WANT TO BE PART OF A HUMAN RIGHTS DELEGATION </s>
<s> WE GOT TO GET INTO THESE AREAS </s>
<s> SO WE WENT IN WHEN THE FIGHTING WAS STILL GOING ON </s>
<s> IT WAS A VERY DIFFICULT SITUATION CONFRONTING THE MEXICAN MILITARY TO PUSH THEM TO OPEN UP TO THE RED CROSS TO OPEN UP TO THE HUMAN RIGHTS COMMUNITY WHICH WE MANAGED TO DO WITHIN TWO WEEKS OF THE FIGHTING STARTING </s>
<s> AND I WAS ALSO JUST VERY I'VE BEEN GOING TO MEXICO FOR YEARS </s>
<s> I'VE BEEN LOOKING INTO THE PLIGHT OF INDIGENOUS PEOPLE FOR YEARS </s>
<s> I'M A NUTRITIONIST BY TRAINING AND WORKED IN MEXICO </s>
<s> IT WAS THE FIRST PLACE I WORKED TWENTY YEARS AGO WITH POOR INDIGENOUS PEOPLE WHO DIDN'T HAVE ENOUGH LAND OR DIDN'T HAVE ENOUGH MONEY TO FEED THEIR KIDS AND I THINK I'VE BEEN SADDENED BY THAT FOR TWENTY YEARS </s>
<s> AND THEN TO SEE THAT KIND OF UPRISING I FELT LIKE I JUST HAD TO BE THERE WATCHING WHAT WAS HAPPENING AND DOING WHAT I COULD DO </s>
<s> AND WHAT DID YOU REPORT BACK </s>
<s> WELL I WAS AMAZED AT THE BRUTALITY OF THE MEXICAN MILITARY DURING THE FIRST TWO WEEKS OF THE FIGHTING </s>
<s> I WAS ALSO AMAZED AT THE ABOUT FACE THAT THE MEXICAN GOVERNMENT DID IN CALLING A UNILATERAL CEASE FIRE CALLING FOR A TRUCE </s>
<s> AND TO ME WHAT IT SHOWS IS THE POWER OF THE MEDIA THE POWER OF THE HUMAN RIGHTS COMMUNITY THE POWER THAT WE AS ORDINARY CITIZENS CAN HAVE WHEN WE DECIDE TO TAKE ACTION ON SOMETHING </s>
<s> SO IT STRENGTHENED THE WHOLE IDEAS THAT I'VE ALWAYS HAD IN CREATING GLOBAL EXCHANGE THAT INDIVIDUAL PEOPLE CAN MAKE HUGE POLICY DIFFERENCES WHEN THEY'RE IN THE RIGHT PLACE AT THE RIGHT TIME </s>
<s> WHAT DO YOU IDENTIFY AS THE ROOT CAUSES OF THE ZAPPATISTA UPRISING </s>
<s> WELL I THINK THE ROOT CAUSES ARE OBVIOUS TO ANYBODY WHO GOES TO MEXICO AND GETS OUT OF THE FANCY HOTEL AREAS AND GOES TO SEE WHAT MEXICO IS LIKE </s>
<s> I JUST READ A REPORT THAT LOOKED AT THE NUMBER OF BILLIONAIRES THAT HAVE BEEN CREATED IN MEXICO IN THE LAST SIX YEARS AND IT'S ABSOLUTELY DISGUSTING </s>
<s> IT'S TERRIBLE BECAUSE YOU SEE BILLIONAIRES IN A COUNTRY WHERE PEOPLE CAN'T EAT THERE'S NOT ENOUGH FOOD FOR PEOPLE THERE'S SUCH INEQUALITIES IN INCOMES IN MEXICO AND THAT'S BEEN EXACERBATED IN THE LAST COUPLE OF YEARS SO THAT MEXICO IS NOW TODAY NUMBER FOUR IN NUMBERS OF BILLIONAIRES </s>
<s> AFTER THE UNITED STATES GERMANY JAPAN COMES MEXICO </s>
<s> AND TO ME THAT SAYS THAT THIS IS SYSTEM THAT IS SO UNEQUAL AND THAT THINGS HAVE TO BE DONE TO HAVE A BETTER DISTRIBUTION OF THE WEALTH THAT'S IN MEXICO </s>
<s> SO UNDERLYING THE CAUSE OF WHY INDIGENOUS PEOPLE IN CHIAPAS ROSE UP IS THE FACT THAT THERE IS SUCH UNEQUAL DISTRIBUTION OF WEALTH IN MEXICO </s>
<s> I READ SOMETHING THAT YOU WROTE AFTER YOU CAME BACK AND I WAS STRUCK BY A MENTION IN THERE OF SOMETHING THAT I REALLY HADN'T SEEN ANYWHERE IN THE U. S. MEDIA ABOUT THE ROLE OF RACISM IN THIS AND THE ROLE OF FEELINGS OF SOME MEXICANS TOWARD THE INDIGENOUS PEOPLE </s>
<s> INDIGENOUS PEOPLE HAVE ALWAYS BEEN TREATED IN A RACIST FASHION IN MEXICO AND IN ALL OF CENTRAL AMERICA AND IN MOST OF THE WORLD </s>
<s> I MEAN CERTAINLY RIGHT HERE IN OUR OWN COUNTRY WE JUST ABOUT DECIMATED THE ENTIRE INDIGENOUS POPULATION IN THIS COUNTRY </s>
<s> SO IT'S NOTHING PARTICULAR TO MEXICO </s>
<s> BUT IN THE CASE OF CHIAPAS WHERE THE UPRISING HAPPENED YOU WALK ALONG MANY OF YOUR LISTENERS HAVE PROBABLY BEEN TO SAN CRISTOBAL DE LAS CASAS BECAUSE IT'S A PRIME TOURIST AREA IN MEXICO AND IT'S A BEAUTIFUL COLONIAL TOWN AND IT'S JUST LOVELY </s>
<s> AND WHAT YOU SEE WHEN YOU GO OUT INTO THE OUTLYING AREAS VERY PICTURESQUE FROM A TOURIST'S POINT OF VIEW BUT WHEN YOU UNDERSTAND WHAT'S MARKING THAT REALITY THAT YOU SEE THESE INDIGENOUS PEOPLE WHO ARE FARMING THESE TINY PIECES OF LAND IN THE MIDDLE OF A SHARP HILL IT'S BECAUSE THE BIG GOOD FLATLANDS HAVE BEEN TAKEN OVER MOSTLY BY NON INDIGENOUS WEALTHY CATTLE RANCHERS THAT HAVE PUSHED THE INDIGENOUS PEOPLE WHO THAT LAND ORIGINALLY BELONGED TO INTO THE WORST LANDS ON THE HILLSIDES </s>
<s> AND THAT HAS LED TO THEM NOT HAVING ENOUGH LAND TO FEED THEIR FAMILIES AND ALSO THAT THERE'S NOT A DECENT EDUCATION SYSTEM FOR INDIGENOUS PEOPLE </s>
<s> THEY'RE NOT TAUGHT IN THEIR INDIGENOUS LANGUAGE </s>
<s> IT'S TO THE POINT THAT IN SOME PLACES IN WALKING ON THE STREETS OF SAN CRISTOBAL YOU WOULD FIND INDIGENOUS PEOPLE GETTING OFF THE SIDEWALKS SO THAT THE WHITE PEOPLE COULD GO BY </s>
<s> IT'S FIVE HUNDRED YEARS OF RACISM AND DESTRUCTION OF INDIGENOUS CULTURE AND I THINK THAT THAT'S ABOUT TIME THAT IT STOPPED </s>
<s> I READ SOMETHING ABOUT THE ZAPPATISTA REBELS COMING OUT OF COMMUNITIES IN SOUTHERN MEXICO THAT IT SORT OF FORGED COLLECTIVE DECISION MAKING CIVIL SOCIETIES </s>
<s> SUBCOMANDANTE MARCOS WHOM YOU MET SAYS THAT THEY'RE NOT INTERESTED IN STATE POWER </s>
<s> YET THOSE ARE MESSAGES THAT I CERTAINLY DIDN'T SEE IN ANY OF THE MAINSTREAM PRESS </s>
<s> EXPLAIN SOME OF THAT AND WHY YOU THINK IT DOESN'T GET REPORTED </s>
<s> WELL UNFORTUNATELY THE U. S. PRESS DOESN'T USUALLY GO INTO A LOT OF ANALYSIS </s>
<s> IT'S USUALLY PRETTY SUPERFICIAL AND I THINK THIS IS A MOVEMENT THAT'S EXTRAORDINARY </s>
<s> I MEAN I DON'T WANT TO PUSH VIOLENCE </s>
<s> I DON'T THINK VIOLENCE IS A SOLUTION </s>
<s> I DON'T LIKE VIOLENCE </s>
<s> I DON'T LIKE THE IDEA OF TAKING UP A GUN AS THE WAY TO FIND A SOLUTION TO SOCIAL ISSUES </s>
<s> I CAN UNDERSTAND WHY PEOPLE GET TO THAT POINT AND I CAN SUPPORT THE ISSUES THAT THEY'RE WORKING TOWARDS </s>
<s> SO I DON'T WANT TO GLORIFY THE VIOLENT ASPECTS OF AN ARMED UPRISING BUT I AM QUITE AMAZED AT HOW PACIFIST IN MANY WAYS THE ZAPPATISTAS ARE </s>
<s> THEY REALLY DON'T BELIEVE THAT VIOLENCE IS THE WAY TO CHANGE </s>
<s> THEY FELT THAT THEY HAD NO CHOICE BUT TO TAKE AN ACTION THAT CAN BE CALLED A VIOLENT ACTION OF TAKING OVER SIX TOWNS IN THE AREA TO CREATE A SPLASH THAT WOULD DRAW WORLD ATTENTION TO THEIR PROBLEMS </s>
<s> IN THE MEANTIME WORLD ATTENTION HAS BEEN DRAWN TO THE PROBLEMS AND THEY DON'T WANT TO GO BACK TO ARMED STRUGGLE </s>
<s> THEY WANT TO FIND PEACEFUL SOLUTIONS AND THEY HAVE BEEN CALLING ON MEXICAN SOCIETY ALL OVER THE COUNTRY TO SAY LET'S LOOK FOR A PEACEFUL ROUTE TO CHANGE </s>
<s> LET'S CALL ON ALL THESE SECTORS OF WHAT THEY CALL CIVIL SOCIETY THE ENVIRONMENTAL COMMUNITY THE WOMEN'S COMMUNITY THE HEALTH COMMUNITY THE TEACHERS LET'S CALL ALL OF THESE GROUPS TOGETHER AND PUT OUR HEADS TOGETHER AND TALK ABOUT HOW WE CAN HAVE A SYSTEM THAT'S MORE DEMOCRATIC AND MORE JUST IN MEXICO </s>
<s> SO IT'S QUITE AMAZING THAT YOU HAVE YOU KNOW WHAT HAS BEEN REPORTED IN THE PRESS HERE AS AN ARMED STRUGGLE THAT REALLY SEES A VERY TRADITIONAL DEMOCRATIC STANCE AS ITS GOAL AND REALLY BELIEVES IN NON VIOLENT SOLUTIONS </s>
<s> ARE YOU TAKING REALITY TOURS TO CHIAPAS STILL </s>
<s> WE TAKE REALITY TOURS CONSTANTLY TO CHIAPAS </s>
<s> THEY ARE ABSOLUTELY FASCINATING </s>
<s> THEY'RE NOT DANGEROUS </s>
<s> IT'S NOT LIKE YOU'RE GOING TO GET SHOT AT </s>
<s> IT'S AN AREA OF A LOT OF TENSION BUT THERE ISN'T THAT KIND OF OPEN SHOOTING GOING ON RIGHT NOW </s>
