<s> MEDICAL NEWS WHEN WE COME BACK </s>
<s> DETERMINING QUICKLY IF SOMEONE HAS HAD A HEART ATTACK </s>
<s> THE MEDICAL SAVINGS COULD BE ENORMOUS </s>
<s> IN AN ERA WHEN MEDICAL ADVANCES ARE ALMOST ALWAYS EXPENSIVE SOMETHING NEW THIS EVENING </s>
<s> DOCTORS HAVE DEVELOPED AN INEXPENSIVE BLOOD TEST TO DETECT WHO HAS AND WHO HAS NOT HAD A HEART ATTACK </s>
<s> AND AS A. B. C.'S GEORGE STRAIT REPORTS THE TEST COULD LEAD TO SIGNIFICANT HEALTH CARE SAVINGS </s>
<s> EACH YEAR FIVE MILLION PATIENTS ARE RUSHED TO HOSPITAL EMERGENCY ROOMS COMPLAINING OF CHEST PAINS </s>
<s> ROUTINELY EACH ARE PUT IN HIGH TECH HIGH COST CORONARY CARE UNITS AND TREATED AS IF THEY HAVE HAD A HEART ATTACK </s>
<s> THE NEW BLOOD TEST COULD HELP RESOLVE A DIFFICULT AND EXPENSIVE DILEMMA SORTING OUT WHICH OF THESE PEOPLE HAS ACTUALLY HAD A HEART ATTACK </s>
<s> THE STANDARD PROCEDURE FOR DOCTORS HAS BEEN TO TEST FOR AN ENZYME RELEASED BY THE HEART DURING AN ATTACK </s>
<s> IT TAKES TWELVE TO TWENTY FOUR HOURS TO GET THE RESULTS </s>
<s> THE NEW TEST MEASURES A DIFFERENT ENZYME ALSO RELEASED BY THE HEART DURING AN ATTACK </s>
<s> BUT THE RESULTS ARE READY IN LESS THAN TWENTY FIVE MINUTES </s>
<s> SINCE FEWER THAN THIRTY PERCENT OF PEOPLE COMPLAINING OF CHEST PAINS ACTUALLY HAVE HEART ATTACKS THE NEW TEST COULD SAVE BILLIONS BY KEEPING DOWN UNNEEDED ADMISSIONS TO EXPENSIVE INTENSIVE CARE UNITS </s>
<s> WE ESTIMATE THAT WE CAN REDUCE THAT DOWN TO ABOUT ONE BILLION DOLLARS TO TWO BILLION DOLLARS </s>
<s> SO IT WOULD BE A SAVINGS OF SOMEWHERE IN THE RANGE OF TWO BILLION DOLLARS TO THREE BILLION DOLLARS A YEAR </s>
<s> A QUICKER DIAGNOSIS ALSO MEANS DOCTORS WILL BE BETTER ABLE TO DECIDE WHICH PATIENTS SHOULD GET POWERFUL ANTI CLOTTING DRUGS </s>
<s> IF THEY ARE GIVEN TO PATIENTS WHO HAVE NOT HAD HEART ATTACKS THEY CAN CAUSE EXTENSIVE HEMORRHAGING </s>
<s> THE TEST HAS BEEN APPROVED BY THE F. D. A. </s>
<s> IT'S EASY TO PERFORM AND INEXPENSIVE </s>
<s> THE MANUFACTURER SAYS FOR NOW THE TESTS ONLY COST TWENTY DOLLARS </s>
<s> GEORGE STRAIT A. B. C. NEWS WASHINGTON </s>
