<s> A BREAKING STORY IN NORTHERN IRELAND THIS MORNING WHERE C. N. N. HAS CONFIRMED THAT A SHORT TIME AGO THE IRISH REPUBLICAN ARMY ANNOUNCED A CEASE FIRE IN ITS GUERRILLA WAR AGAINST THE BRITISH GOVERNMENT </s>
<s> C. N. N.'S JIM CLANCY IS IN BELFAST NORTHERN IRELAND </s>
<s> HE JOINS US BY PHONE </s>
<s> GOOD MORNING JIM </s>
<s> LESS THAN ONE HOUR AGO THE PROVISIONAL IRISH REPUBLICAN ARMY ANNOUNCED THAT IT HAD ORDERED ALL OF ITS UNITS TO OBSERVE THE COMPLETE CESSATION OF ALL MILITARY OPERATIONS BEGINNING AT MIDNIGHT TONIGHT </s>
<s> IN A STATEMENT THAT WAS ISSUED BY THE I. R. A. IT SAYS IT REMAINS COMMITTED TO THE NATIONALIST CAUSE IT SUPPORTED IT SALUTED ALL OF ITS VOLUNTEERS ITS SUPPORTERS AND ITS POLITICAL PRISONERS </s>
<s> BUT IT SAID THE ATMOSPHERE FOR A JUST AND LASTING SETTLEMENT HAD BEEN CREATED SAYING IT WAS A HISTORIC MOMENT THE I. R. A. SAID IT WOULD DO ALL IT COULD GIVE ALL OF ITS ENERGY DETERMINATION AND PATIENCE TO THE CAUSE OF PEACE HOPING TO BRING ALL SIDES INTO NEGOTIATIONS THAT COULD WORK OUT A POLITICAL SETTLEMENT FOR DECADES OF VIOLENCE IN NORTHERN IRELAND </s>
<s> IT SAID THAT THE DOWNING STREET DECLARATION WAS NOT A SOLUTION AND IT RECOGNIZED IT WAS NOT PRESENTED AS SUCH </s>
<s> INSTEAD THAT DECLARATION PROVIDED THE FRAMEWORK FOR NEGOTIATIONS THAT COULD BRING ABOUT A CHANGE IN THE SITUATION HERE A NEW SITUATION AS THE I. R. A. CALLED IT AN HISTORIC CROSSROAD </s>
<s> THE I. R. A. SAID THAT IT DID NOT SAY HOWEVER THAT THIS WAS GOING TO BE A PERMANENT CEASE FIRE </s>
<s> THAT WAS INSTANTLY CEASED UPON BY THE CRITICS AMONG THE OVERWHELMINGLY PROTESTANT UNIONIST PARTIES HERE </s>
<s> WHILE THEY HAILED THE ANNOUNCEMENT AS THE FIRST STEP THEY WARNED THAT THE I. R. A. DID NOT USE THAT WORD PERMANENT. THEY SAID THEY WANTED TO SEE THE I. R. A. HAND IN ITS GUNS AND EXPLOSIVES </s>
<s> THEY EVEN SUGGESTED THAT THERE COULD BE NO NEGOTIATIONS SO LONG AS THE I. R. A. REMAINED ARMED </s>
<s> THEY ALSO SUSPECT THE CONCESSIONS HAVE BEEN GRANTED BY THE MAJOR GOVERNMENT IN BRITAIN </s>
<s> THEY ACCUSED JOHN MAJOR OF LYING AND PERHAPS SELLING OUT THEIR CONSTITUTION HERE OFFERING THE I. R. A. CONCESSIONS THAT THE UNIONISTS WOULD NOT AGREE TO </s>
<s> JAMES MULLINEAUX THE HEAD OF THE ULTRA UNIONIST PARTY TOOK A CAUTIOUS NOTE SAYING HE HOPED IT WOULD BE A BEGINNING TO A PERMANENT END OF VIOLENCE HERE </s>
<s> MEANWHILE GERRY ADAMS HEAD OF SINN FEIN BELIEVED TO BE THE POLITICAL WING OF THE I. R. A. PRAISED THE I. R. A. ANNOUNCEMENT AS COURAGEOUS </s>
<s> HE CALLED ON BRITAIN TO SEIZE THIS OPPORTUNITY </s>
<s> MEANTIME MORE MODERATES HERE IN NORTHERN ISLAND ON THE POLITICAL SCENE LIKE JOHN ALDERDICE OF THE ALLIANCE PARTY SAID THAT THE ANNOUNCEMENT WAS ONE THAT ALL OF NORTHERN ISLAND HAD BEEN WAITING FOR </s>
<s> THIS WAS INDEED A HISTORIC DAY </s>
<s> AND HE CALLED ON PROTESTANT PARAMILITARIES TO JOIN IN THE CEASE FIRE </s>
<s> HOWEVER THERE HAS BEEN A SWIFT RESPONSE FROM THE PARAMILITARIES THEY SAY THEY'RE NOT GOING TO HAVE ANY COMMENT UNTIL THEY HERE FROM DOWNING STREET ABOUT THE POSSIBILITY THAT SOME SECRET CONCESSIONS WERE GIVEN TO THE I. R. A. IN ORDER TO OBTAIN THIS CEASE FIRE </s>
<s> BUT THE CEASE FIRE ON ITS FACE DOES ONE THING THAT CANNOT BE DISPUTED </s>
<s> IT OPENS UP THE PROCESS </s>
<s> IT MAKES IT POSSIBLE FOR NEGOTIATIONS TO GO AHEAD IF THE UNIONIST PARTIES ARE WILLING TO DO THAT </s>
<s> IT PROVIDES AN HISTORIC OPPORTUNITY FOR NORTHERN IRELAND TO TURN AWAY FROM THE CYCLE OF VIOLENCE AND TO PRODUCE SOME KIND OF A LASTING SETTLEMENT HERE IN NORTHERN IRELAND </s>
<s> I'M JIM CLANCY REPORTING LIVE FROM BELFAST </s>
<s> JIM IN THE PAST THERE HAVE BEEN MANY SHOT LIVED TRUCES </s>
<s> ANY INDICATION THAT THIS ONE WILL LAST </s>
<s> CERTAINLY THERE IS A LOT OF PRESSURE ON ALL SIDES HERE TO MAKE THIS DEAL WORK </s>
<s> THE I. R. A. IN ITS STATEMENT TODAY SAID THAT IT WAS GOING TO GIVE ALL OF ITS DETERMINATION IT WAS GOING TO GIVE ALL OF ITS ENERGY TO MAKING IT WORK AND MOST OF ALL IT SAID IT WAS GOING TO GIVE ALL OF ITS PATIENCE TO MAKING THIS DEAL WORK </s>
<s> SO WHAT WE HAVE HERE IS THE SITUATION WHERE THOUGH ITS NOT PERFECTLY DEFINED IT SEEMS TO BE BETTER DEFINED THAN EVEN THE OPPONENTS OF THE I. R. A. HAD EVEN HOPED FOR </s>
