<s> BUT WHEN THE FIRE OCCURRED THE LEGISLATIVE RESPONSE WAS TO PASS SOME LAWS AND TO BEGIN ESSENTIALLY THE BEGINNINGS OF MINNESOTA'S FORESTRY PROGRAM </s>
<s> IN PARTICULAR THERE WERE LAWS PASSED ABOUT THE PROPER DISPOSAL OF SLASH PILES LAWS WHICH REMAIN ON THE BOOKS TODAY </s>
