<s> FOR ONE THING MANY PEOPLE SAY THE AGENCY'S VERY STRUCTURE IS FUNDAMENTALLY FLAWED </s>
<s> IT'S DESIGNED REALLY TO CREATE POLICY PARALYSIS </s>
<s> ERNEST GALHORN IS A MEMBER OF A GROUP CALLED THE ADMINISTRATIVE CONFERENCE OF THE UNITED STATES </s>
<s> BASICALLY IT ADVISES FEDERAL AGENCIES ON WHICH OF THEIR PROCEDURES WORK AND WHICH DON'T </s>
<s> GALHORN IS A KIND OF STUDENT OF BUREAUCRACIES AND HE SAYS THE F. E. C. IS A PRIME EXAMPLE OF WHAT DOESN'T WORK </s>
<s> THIS IS A SCHEME THAT MACHIAVELLI WOULD BE PROUD OF BECAUSE IT FOCUSES ON THE MINUTIA AND IT GUARANTEES THAT THE COMMISSION CANNOT TAKE SIGNIFICANT ACTION </s>
<s> UNLIKE OTHER INDEPENDENT REGULATORY BODIES THE F. E. C. HAS AN EVEN NUMBER OF COMMISSIONERS THREE REPUBLICANS AND THREE DEMOCRATS AND IT TAKES FOUR VOTES A TWO THIRDS MAJORITY TO DO ANYTHING </s>
<s> POLITICALLY THIS HAS TWO RESULTS </s>
<s> ON THE POSITIVE SIDE WHEN THE COMMISSION FINDS SOMEONE VIOLATED THE CAMPAIGN LAWS THE VIOLATOR KNOWS IT WAS A BIPARTISAN DECISION NOT JUST A POLITICAL ATTACK FROM THE OTHER SIDE OF THE AISLE </s>
<s> BUT IT ALSO MEANS THAT EACH PARTY CAN VETO ANY INVESTIGATION OR AUDIT IT FEELS UNCOMFORTABLE WITH </s>
<s> IN THE PAST TWO YEARS THE COMMISSION HASN'T GRIDLOCKED VERY OFTEN TWENTY TIMES IN SEVEN HUNDRED SEVENTY EIGHT VOTES ACCORDING TO FIGURES SUPPLIED BY THE F. E. C. </s>
<s> BUT PUBLIC INTEREST GROUPS LIKE F. E. C. WATCH AND COMMON CAUSE SAY IT DOESN'T TAKE MANY DEADLOCK VOTES TO LEAVE THE IMPRESSION THAT THE COMMISSION IS HAMSTRUNG </s>
<s> ELIZABETH HEADLAND IS WITH F. E. C. WATCH </s>
