<s> BUT THE PEOPLE IN MIDDLE THE BIG LARGE NUMBER OF PEOPLE IN THE MIDDLE BETWEEN THOSE TWO CLASSES CAN'T AFFORD TO GO TO A HOSPITAL AND THEY CAN'T AFFORD TO PAY WHAT IT COSTS SOMETIMES AND THEY CAN'T AFFORD SOMETIMES EVEN TO PAY THE DOCTOR BILL AFTER THEY GET SERVICE </s>
