<s> IN THE LATE NINETEEN SIXTIES EARLY NINETEEN SEVENTIES TED KENNEDY IN PARTICULAR BUT ALSO OTHER DEMOCRATS WERE PROPOSING NATIONAL HEALTH INSURANCE AND RICHARD NIXON WAS RESPONDING TO THAT </s>
