<s> THERE'S RISK IN A MUTUAL FUND ESPECIALLY IF YOU DON'T KNOW MUCH ABOUT THE FUND ITSELF </s>
<s> HOW MUCH IMPACT DOES A PROSPECTUS PROVIDE </s>
<s> KELLI ARENA HAS SOME TIPS TO HELP SQUEEZE THE JUICE OUT OF THE JARGON AND MAKE IT A BIT EASIER </s>
<s> SINCE THE MUTUAL FUND INDUSTRY BEGAN SEVENTY YEARS AGO MORE THAN A MILLION TREES HAVE FALLEN IN ORDER TO PRINT PROSPECTUSES </s>
<s> THOSE ARE THE BOOKLETS LEGALLY REQUIRED TO DESCRIBE THE FUNDS IN DETAIL </s>
<s> SOME FORTY MILLION AMERICANS OWN MUTUAL FUNDS INVESTING MORE THAN TWO TRILLION DOLLARS </s>
<s> THAT'S A LOT OF PROSPECTUS READING BUT WHAT DOES A PROSPECTUS REALLY SAY </s>
<s> THE PROSPECTUSES ARE SO UNILLUMINATING OFTEN OBSCURE THAT THEY'RE CONFUSING UNSOPHISTICATED INVESTORS </s>
<s> INVESTORS ARE OFTEN BAFFLED BY THE PAGES OF PRINT SIMPLY BECAUSE THEIR EYES GLAZE OVER </s>
<s> OVER THE YEARS PROSPECTUSES HAVE EVOLVED INTO INCREDIBLY LEGALISTIC DOCUMENTS THAT UNLESS YOU'RE TRULY DILIGENT IT'S HARD TO GET THROUGH IT </s>
<s> NEW YORK CITY OFFICIALS RECENTLY DID A STUDY OF THIRTY TYPICAL MUTUAL FUND PROSPECTUSES </s>
<s> HERE IS A VANGUARD WINDSOR PROSPECTUS ON THE ISSUE OF RISK COMMON STOCKS WILL DECLINE OVER SHORT OR EXTENDED PERIODS </s>
<s> DECLINE THEY ACTUALLY SAY THE WORD </s>
<s> IT COULD GO DOWN </s>
<s> HERE'S PRUDENTIAL GROWTH FUND </s>
<s> A LOT OF WORDS HERE NOT A WORD THAT YOU COULD LOSE YOUR MONEY </s>
<s> HERE IS A TEMPLETON GROWTH FUND WHICH IN A VERY LAUDIBLE WAY EXPLICITLY SAYS SHARES OF THIS FUND ARE NOT DEPOSITS GUARANTEED BY ANY BANK </s>
<s> COMPARE THAT WITH THE EUROPACIFIC GROWTH FUND WHICH IS RELEASED AND PUBLISHED BY CHEMICAL BANK </s>
<s> A LOT OF PEOPLE WOULD ASSUME IT WAS PUBLISHED BY A BANK IT MUST BE F. D. I. C. INSURED </s>
<s> IT'S NOT AND NOWHERE HERE DOES IT SAY THAT IT'S NOT F. D. I. C. INSURED </s>
<s> FUND PROSPECTUSES DO MEET MINIMUM LEGAL REQUIREMENTS BUT THE FAST GROWING INDUSTRY SAYS THAT IT'S TRYING TO DO BETTER </s>
<s> PROSPECTUS DISCLOSURE IS ALWAYS BEING IMPROVED AND IF YOU LOOK AT FUND ACTUAL PROSPECTUSES THERE'S BETTER DISCLOSURE NOW </s>
