<s> ITS CAUSE STILL IS A SUBJECT OF SHARP DEBATE BUT THE DEBATE RECENTLY HAS TAKEN A NEW TURN </s>
<s> C. N. N. MEDICAL CORRESPONDENT ANDREW HOLTZ CONTINUES HIS SERIES ADVANCING ON ALZHEIMER'S </s>
<s> YOU SEE THESE CELL FIBERS </s>
<s> THIS IS A NERVE CELL FROM A PATIENT WITH ALZHEIMER'S DISEASE </s>
<s> WHEN THE CELL DIES YOU HAVE A CAST OF THESE CELL FIBERS PRESENT AND THE CELL IS GONE </s>
<s> SO THIS WE FEEL IS PROBABLY WHAT THE IS THE IMMEDIATE CAUSE OF DEMENTIA </s>
<s> BUT WHY DO ALZHEIMER'S PATIENTS HAVE THESE FIBERS MADE OF WHAT'S CALLED BETA AMALOID PROTEIN </s>
<s> THEY MAY BE LACKING AN ENZYME THAT WOULD CLEAVE THE BETA PROTEIN AND INACTIVATE IT AND MAKE IT IMPOSSIBLE TO FORM FIBERS </s>
<s> THIS THEORY SUGGESTS ENZYMES MIGHT BE A KEY TO TREATING THE DISEASE </s>
<s> LABORATORY STUDIES INDICATE BETA AMALOID PRODUCES CHEMICALS CALLED FREE RADICALS THAT CAN KILL NERVE CELLS </s>
<s> IT WOULD INDICATE THAT EATING A GOOD DIET RICH IN ANTI OXIDANTS MAYBE TAKING SUPPLEMENTS VITAMIN E. VITAMIN C. THIS TYPE OF THING WOULD BE IMPORTANT </s>
<s> BUT SOME RESEARCHERS BELIEVE BETA AMALOID IS A </s>
<s> BY PRODUCT OF THE DISEASE AND A DISTRACTION TO RESEARCH </s>
<s> SMUDGES ON FILM ARE PART OF A HOT NEW LEAD </s>
<s> THEY SHOW DIFFERENT FORMS OF A GENE CALLED APOLIPOPROTEIN E. APO E. FOR SHORT </s>
<s> PEOPLE WITH ONE COMBINATION OF APO E. GENES TEND TO GET ALZHEIMER'S AS MUCH AS TWENTY YEARS EARLIER THAN PEOPLE WITH A DIFFERENT COMBINATION </s>
<s> NO MATTER WHAT ELSE WE PREVIOUSLY THOUGHT ABOUT ALZHEIMER'S DISEASE WE HAVE TO LOOK AT WHAT THE ROLE OF APO E. IS IN THE METABOLISM OF CELLS THAT LEADS TO ALZHEIMER'S DISEASE </s>
