<s> YOU COULDN'T HAVE TWO MORE DIVERSE CULTURES WHEN MONKS FOR THE DALAI LAMA'S NONGALM MONASTERY JOIN CHILDREN FROM WATTS </s>
<s> THE RESULT WAS ABSOLUTELY FASCINATING </s>
<s> GLORIA HILLARD HAS THIS STORY </s>
<s> WATTS WHERE THE WALLS ARE OFTEN THE CANVAS OF THE CHOICE AND SPRAY PAINT THE ARTIST'S TOOL CHILDREN WERE LEARNING THE SACRED ART OF SAND PAINTING </s>
<s> ALONGSIDE FOR MONKS FROM TIBET THEY WERE LEARNING TO CREATE A MANDALA A BUDDHIST RITUAL THAT DATES BACK TO SIX HUNDRED B. C. </s>
<s> THIS IS THE FIRST TIME THAT THIS PROJECT HAS EVER BEEN DONE WHERE THE CHILDREN ARE ACTUALLY COMING AND LEARNING ABOUT THE TRADITION LEARNING HOW TO MAKE THE SAND MANDALA AND MAKING ONE THEMSELVES </s>
<s> THIS HAS NEVER BEEN DONE EVER </s>
<s> SO FOR ONE MONTH THEY WORK SIDE BY SIDE </s>
<s> IN ONE ROOM THE MONKS CREATED THE WHEEL OF COMPASSION WHICH THEY BELIEVE IS THE HOME OF ENLIGHTENED BEINGS OF COMPASSION </s>
<s> THE MOSAIC IMAGES OF THE COLORED SAND ARE AS INTRICATE AS EMBROIDERED SILK </s>
<s> FOR SIX HOURS A DAY THEY WORKED SO DID THE CHILDREN CREATING THEIR OWN MANDALA </s>
<s> FROM THIS I THINK THEY CAN LEARN A LITTLE BIT ABOUT CONCENTRATION AND DISCIPLINE AND RESPECT AND COMPASSION </s>
<s> IT'S HELPED WITH MY MEDITATING </s>
<s> LIKE WHEN I'M IN TIGHT SITUATIONS IT'S BEEN EASIER TO GET OF ET CETERA ET CETERA </s>
<s> I LEARNED YOU HAVE TO BE GENTLE </s>
<s> I ENJOYED IT </s>
<s> IT KEPT ME CALM AND RELAXED </s>
<s> I STAYED OUT OF TROUBLE </s>
<s> THE PROJECT WAS CALLED HEALING THE CAUSES OF VIOLENCE THROUGH ART </s>
<s> EACH DAY AS THE MONKS FORMED A CIRCLE AROUND THE MANDALA THEY PRAYED FOR PEACE BELIEVING THEN THAT THE SPIRIT OF THAT INTENTION IS SENT OUT INTO THE COMMUNITY </s>
<s> THIS WILL NOW MAKE A MORE PEACEFUL COMMUNITY IN THE FUTURE </s>
<s> AND THEN IN KEEPING WITH TIBETAN TRADITION THE MANDALA IS DISMANTLED SWEPT UP </s>
<s> THE COLORED SAND IS THEN TAKEN TO THE OCEAN AND RELEASED WITH THE ESSENCE OF THE COMPASSION TO RETURN ONCE AGAIN TO THE NEIGHBORHOOD WHERE IT ALL BEGAN </s>
